Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-波比  -暴风女\N{\rDefault Eng}- Bobby. - Hey, Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  小鬼\N{\rDefault Eng}Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您来了\N{\rDefault Eng}You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要哨兵发动袭击\N{\rDefault Eng}Whenever the Sentinels attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战戟就能发现它们\N{\rDefault Eng}Warpath spots them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我把毕肖普送回过去\N{\rDefault Eng}And I sent Bishop back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在袭击发生前警告我们\N{\rDefault Eng}to warn us of the attack before it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪烁搜索到下一个安全点  然后...\N{\rDefault Eng}Blink scouts the next site and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在它们发现之前我们就离开了\N{\rDefault Eng}Well then we leave before they ever know we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们从未出现在那里\N{\rDefault Eng}Because we never were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫你们从未出现在那里\N{\rDefault Eng}What do you mean you were never there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把毕肖普送回到几天前\N{\rDefault Eng}She projects Bishop back in time few days
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒其他人将会发生这次袭击\N{\rDefault Eng}to warn the others of the coming attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能让毕肖普回到过去\N{\rDefault Eng}She sends Bishop back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是他的意识\N{\rDefault Eng}No, just his consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了更年轻的自己身上\N{\rDefault Eng}in to his younger-self, into his younger body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害\N{\rDefault Eng}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也许行得通  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}This might just work, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么行得通\N{\rDefault Eng}What might work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哨兵计划\N{\rDefault Eng}The Sentinel Program
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初是由玻利瓦尔·特拉斯克博士策划的\N{\rDefault Eng}was originally conceived by Dr. Bolivar Trask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在70年代早期\N{\rDefault Eng}In the early 70s
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是全球首屈一指的武器设计师\N{\rDefault Eng}he was one of the world-leading weapons designers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但暗地里  他开始在变种人身上进行实验\N{\rDefault Eng}But covertly he had begun experimenting on mutants,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用他们的天赋来辅助他的研究\N{\rDefault Eng}using their gifts to fuel his own research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个变种人发现了他的所作所为\N{\rDefault Eng}There was one mutant who had discovered what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个能够变身成任何人的变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}A mutant with the ability to transform herself into anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔形女\N{\rDefault Eng}Mystique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识的她叫瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}I knew her as Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们少时相遇  并一起长大\N{\rDefault Eng}We met when we were children, grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就像是我的妹妹\N{\rDefault Eng}She was like a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着帮助她\N{\rDefault Eng}I tried to help her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却反令她与我渐行渐远\N{\rDefault Eng}but only succeeded in driving her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.22,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在全球范围内追杀特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}She hunted Trask across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1973年  美国侵越战争结束后  \N{\rDefault Eng}And at the Paris Peace Accords in 1973
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在签订巴黎和平协定时\N{\rDefault Eng}after the Vietnam War,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她找到了特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}she found Trask,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并杀了他\N{\rDefault Eng}and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是她第一次杀人\N{\rDefault Eng}It was the first time she killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是最后一次\N{\rDefault Eng}Wasn't her last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但杀死特拉斯克并没有带来她预期的结果\N{\rDefault Eng}But killing Trask did not have the outcome she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而令政府看到了这个计划的必要性\N{\rDefault Eng}It only persuaded the government of the need for his program.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  他们抓住了她\N{\rDefault Eng}They captured her that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她进行折磨和实验\N{\rDefault Eng}Tortured her. Experimented on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她的DNA中\N{\rDefault Eng}In her DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们发现了她变形能力的秘密\N{\rDefault Eng}they discovered the secret to her powers of transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这为他们提供了关键信息\N{\rDefault Eng}It gave them the key they needed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们制造出了能适应任何变种力量的武器\N{\rDefault Eng}to create weapons that could adapt to any mutant power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不到50年的时间里\N{\rDefault Eng}And in less than 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那毁灭过无数变种人的机器就问世了\N{\rDefault Eng}the machines that have destroyed so many of our kind were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都始于1973年那一天\N{\rDefault Eng}And it all started that day in 1973,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她首开杀戮的那天\N{\rDefault Eng}the day she first killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真正成为魔形女的那天\N{\rDefault Eng}the day she truly became Mystique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想回到那时候\N{\rDefault Eng}You wanna go back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我可以找到她\N{\rDefault Eng}If I can get to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止这场暗杀\N{\rDefault Eng}stop the assassination,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她远离他们的魔爪\N{\rDefault Eng}keep her out of their hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就能阻止哨兵的出现\N{\rDefault Eng}then we can stop the Sentinels from ever being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将这场战争扼杀在摇篮里\N{\rDefault Eng}And end this war before it ever begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以把一个人送回几周前\N{\rDefault Eng}I can send someone back a couple of weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许一个月前  但你们说的是几十年\N{\rDefault Eng}maybe a month, but you're talking about going back decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授  您拥有全世界最强的大脑\N{\rDefault Eng}You have the most powerful brain the world, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但意识被拉扯到极限时就会断裂\N{\rDefault Eng}But the mind can only stretch so far before it snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会毁掉您的  抱歉\N{\rDefault Eng}It will rip you apart. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能在这种旅行中存活\N{\rDefault Eng}No one can survive that trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人的意识即使断裂了也能恢复呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What if someone's mind has a way of snapping back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果断裂之后马上就能自愈呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What if someone can heal as fast as they're ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  散开吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Okay, spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位\N{\rDefault Eng}Take you positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在过去的我身上醒来  鬼知道会在哪\N{\rDefault Eng}So I wake up in the my younger body god knows where,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\rDefault Eng}then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要到我家去找我\N{\rDefault Eng}You'll need to go to my house and find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说服我相信这一切\N{\rDefault Eng}Convince me of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能直接读我的心吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Wouldn't you just be able to read my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1973年的我失去了这种能力\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't have my powers in 1973.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗根  你要像我曾帮助你那样帮助我\N{\rDefault Eng}Logan, you're going to have to do for me what I once did for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导我  指引我\N{\rDefault Eng}Lead me. Guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我和现在大相庭径 \N{\rDefault Eng}I was a very different man then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对我有耐心\N{\rDefault Eng}You'll have to be patient with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耐心可不是我的特长\N{\rDefault Eng}Patience isn't my strongest suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会需要我\N{\rDefault Eng}You'll need me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔形女离开查尔斯后就和我一起\N{\rDefault Eng}After Mystique left Charles, she came with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送她走上了一条危险的道路\N{\rDefault Eng}and I set her on a dangerous path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更黑暗的道路\N{\rDefault Eng}Darker path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然咱们两个是敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}It's going to take the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在需要并肩作战了\N{\rDefault Eng}side by side at a time when we couldn't be further apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了\N{\rDefault Eng}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要去哪儿找你\N{\rDefault Eng}So where do I find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...有点复杂\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh...It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说  你的意识回到过去时\N{\rDefault Eng}Basically your body will go to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体会进入睡眠状态\N{\rDefault Eng}while your mind travels back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那边时\N{\rDefault Eng}As long as you're back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去和现在将继续共存\N{\rDefault Eng}past and present will continue to coexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦你醒来...\N{\rDefault Eng}But once you wake up....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做出的任何改变都将生效并成为历史\N{\rDefault Eng}whatever you've done will take hold and become history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们其他人来说\N{\rDefault Eng}And for the rest of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那将是我们唯一知晓的历史\N{\rDefault Eng}that will be the only history that we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像过去的50年从未发生一样\N{\rDefault Eng}That will be like, the last 50 years never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界  这场战争\N{\rDefault Eng}This world. This war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一会记住这件事的人\N{\rDefault Eng}The only person who'll remember it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你\N{\rDefault Eng}is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  罗根  我需要你整理思绪\N{\rDefault Eng}Alright Logan, I need you to clear your head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量保持平静\N{\rDefault Eng}and to stay as calm as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  什么意思\N{\rDefault Eng}What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你情绪变激动  我将很难稳住你\N{\rDefault Eng}If your mind gets rocky, it will be harder for me to hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会在过去和未来之间漂泊不定\N{\rDefault Eng}You could start to slip between past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不得不激动呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What if I need to get a little rocky ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想点平和的想法吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Think peaceful thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平和的想法\N{\rDefault Eng}Peaceful thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么好消息吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Do you have any good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\rDefault Eng}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会变老所以当时的你长得跟现在差不多\N{\rDefault Eng}you don't really age so you'll pretty much look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会有太多时间留在过去\N{\rDefault Eng}You won't have much time in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哨兵会找到我们  一如既往\N{\rDefault Eng}Sentinels will find us, they always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这次我们既跑不了也逃不掉了\N{\rDefault Eng}And this time we won't be able to run or have no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最后的机会\N{\rDefault Eng}This is our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真认为这能行吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You really think this will work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信他\N{\rDefault Eng}I have faith in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心的不是他  是我们\N{\rDefault Eng}It's not him I'm worried about. It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那时还年轻  不知好歹\N{\rDefault Eng}We were young, we didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该知道了\N{\rDefault Eng}We will now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家待会见\N{\rDefault Eng}See you all soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会有点疼\N{\rDefault Eng}It might sting a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我靠\N{\rDefault Eng}Holy Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真成功了\N{\rDefault Eng}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了\N{\rDefault Eng}Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-格温  把衣服穿上  -你他妈是谁\N{\rDefault Eng}- Gwen! Get dressed! - Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我不知道怎么回事\N{\rDefault Eng}Hey, I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是\N{\rDefault Eng}What's going on is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该保护老大的女儿\N{\rDefault Eng}you supposed to be guarding your boss's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是和她乱搞\N{\rDefault Eng}not screwing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没跟她睡\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't sleep with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有  -没有\N{\rDefault Eng}- No? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我确实跟她睡过好几次  但是\N{\rDefault Eng}I mean, yes I slept with her many times, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:18:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉米\N{\rDefault Eng}Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我  那是原来的我\N{\rDefault Eng}That wasn't me. That was the old me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这个我大概20秒前才到  -是吗\N{\rDefault Eng}- I just got here like 20 seconds ago. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是啊  -那你的衣服呢\N{\rDefault Eng}- Yeah. - And what happened to your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...这...\N{\rDefault Eng}No...Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你\N{\rDefault Eng}Would you believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来自未来  你会信吗\N{\rDefault Eng}if I told you I was sent here from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  先出去吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Get out of here, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小丑我们来处理\N{\rDefault Eng}We'll take care of this comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你处理不了的\N{\rDefault Eng}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会把你的车钥匙和汽油钱都给我\N{\rDefault Eng}You're gonna give me the keys of your car and some money for gas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则你会在医院里醒来\N{\rDefault Eng}or you're gonna wake up in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我知道这种事会怎么收尾\N{\rDefault Eng}Trust me, I know how these things play out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你来自未来吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Because you're from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  因为这个\N{\rDefault Eng}No, because of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活见鬼了\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rDefault Eng}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平和的想法\N{\rDefault Eng}Peaceful thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在评估各种国防支出\N{\rDefault Eng}We are reviewing all of our defense expenditures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的黑名册都被查看过了\N{\rDefault Eng}and all the black books are being opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能资助一种会对付我国公民的武器\N{\rDefault Eng}We can't support a weapon that targets our own citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这些变种人真如你所说\N{\rDefault Eng}If these mutants as you described,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经生活在我们身边\N{\rDefault Eng}are already living among us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他们也是在平和地生活着\N{\rDefault Eng}then they are living here peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年内一起事故都没有发生过\N{\rDefault Eng}We haven't had an incident in over 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古巴那事就不算吗\N{\rDefault Eng}After what happened in Cuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事从来没被确认过\N{\rDefault Eng}That was never confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在外有真正的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}We have very real enemies out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯人  中国人\N{\rDefault Eng}The Russians, the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在说的是\N{\rDefault Eng}We're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人口中的九牛一毛\N{\rDefault Eng}a tenth of a tenth of a tenth of our population.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请让我为你们念一段话  -请吧\N{\rDefault Eng}- Allow me to read something to you. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们中情局的朋友们获取的\N{\rDefault Eng}This was acquired by our friends at the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一部毕业论文\N{\rDefault Eng}It's a dissertation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由牛津大学的一位变种人所写\N{\rDefault Eng}written by a mutant at Oxford University.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我引用他的话\N{\rDefault Eng}And I quote:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"对于尼安德特人来说\N{\rDefault Eng}"To Homo neanderthalensis,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他的变种亲属  现代智人\N{\rDefault Eng}"his mutant cousin Homo sapiens,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我们\N{\rDefault Eng}which is us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"是一种畸变"\N{\rDefault Eng}"was an aberration".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"变种现代智人的到来\N{\rDefault Eng}"The arrival of the mutated human species Homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"导致了\N{\rDefault Eng}"was followed by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"其进化相对缓慢的同类的即时灭绝"\N{\rDefault Eng}"the immediate extinction of their less evolved kin".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rDefault Eng}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rDefault Eng}now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就相当于尼安德特人\N{\rDefault Eng}we are the Neanderthals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以偏概全  特拉斯克博士\N{\rDefault Eng}Speak for yourself, Dr. Trask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初你们把我们的军队送去越南\N{\rDefault Eng}You know, when you send our soldiers to Vietnam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不给他们装备能打胜仗的武器\N{\rDefault Eng}without the weapon they needed to win the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你们低估了敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}you underestimated your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们也低估这个敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}You do that with this enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后果将不再是地球另一端的边境冲突\N{\rDefault Eng}it won't be some border skirmish halfway around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的街道  城市和家园都将成为战场\N{\rDefault Eng}This time the war will be for our streets, our cities, our homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你们意识到我的计划的必要性时\N{\rDefault Eng}And by the time you see the need for my program,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都将来不及了\N{\rDefault Eng}it will be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们这辈子  会输掉两场战争\N{\rDefault Eng}And you will have lost two wars in one life time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  特拉斯克博士\N{\rDefault Eng}We're sorry, Dr. Trask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哨兵计划\N{\rDefault Eng}But your Sentinel Program,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会被采纳的\N{\rDefault Eng}it ain't gonna fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20\b0\pos(192,215)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,863,\alpha0)\t(2485,3115,\alpha&HFF&)}西  贡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有事吗  上校\N{\rDefault Eng}Can I help you, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给我的孩子们好好道个别\N{\rDefault Eng}Just here to give my boys a proper send off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉长官  但我们有命令  \N{\rDefault Eng}I'm sorry, sir. But we have orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是隔离区\N{\rDefault Eng}This is a quarantined area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  士兵  这是命令\N{\rDefault Eng}Stand aside, soldier. That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立正\N{\rDefault Eng}Attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\rDefault Eng}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验报告  验血报告\N{\rDefault Eng}Lab reports, blood tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部准备打包送回去\N{\rDefault Eng}It's all getting packed up and shipped back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送到哪里去\N{\rDefault Eng}Where is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也会去的地方\N{\rDefault Eng}Same place as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特拉斯克企业\N{\rDefault Eng}Trask Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\frz346.025\pos(108,90)\fad(330,0)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs15\xbord1\blur5\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\3c&H5783A2&}特拉斯克企业  绝密  \N亚历山大·萨默斯  1973年1月21日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  先生们\N{\rDefault Eng}Let's go, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你们离开这个鬼地方\N{\rDefault Eng}Taking you out of this shit show.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Shipping home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时不回\N{\rDefault Eng}Not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些是干什么的\N{\rDefault Eng}What are you doing with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会令我们的旅途更平稳\N{\rDefault Eng}It's gonna make the ride a little smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要把你们转移到一个私人机构\N{\rDefault Eng}We are transferring you to a private facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里我们可以...再做几项测试\N{\rDefault Eng}where we can...run a few more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是军队的人\N{\rDefault Eng}Your men are not military.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私人机构  我们授权遣送这些人\N{\rDefault Eng}Private outfit. We're authorized to remand these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人要回家\N{\rDefault Eng}These troops are going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  上校...\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这事不在你的管辖范围内\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't believe you have jurisdiction in this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我管得着  孩子\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm afraid I do, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  你是谁\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm sorry. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是  少校\N{\rDefault Eng}The question is, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz321.512\pos(259,155)}{\fad(330,0)\fn方正黑体简体\fs15\b1\xbord2\blur5\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HA7D1EF&}小威廉·史崔克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.92,0:24:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\rDefault Eng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.42,0:24:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.77,0:24:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我的名字\N{\rDefault Eng}That's not my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我搞得定  -我知道\N{\rDefault Eng}- I had that. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出去吧  快点  我们走\N{\rDefault Eng}Let's move out. Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.00,0:25:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克呢\N{\rDefault Eng}Where's Erik?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.22,0:25:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在单干了\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm on my own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.53,0:25:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  动起来\N{\rDefault Eng}Let's go. Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别起飞\N{\rDefault Eng}Hold that plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.90,0:25:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想让这些孩子留在这个倒霉的国家\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't wanna leave these boys in this godforsaken country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不跟我们一起走了  是吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You're not coming with us, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.87,0:25:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的仗还没打完  敌人还在四处横行\N{\rDefault Eng}My war is not over. The enemy is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.25,0:26:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去哪儿了\N{\rDefault Eng}Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.10,0:26:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那四个二等兵  他们去哪儿了\N{\rDefault Eng}The four privates. Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.41,0:26:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们朝停机坪去了\N{\rDefault Eng}They were heading towards the tarmac.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\move(107,187,132,176,2197,5867)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\xbord2\shad0\blur5\alpha&HFF&\t(0,2656,\alpha0)\c&H5A777D&\3c&H151D18&\t(2197,5867,\fs21)}私宅\N闲人免入
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.12,0:26:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,41)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}泽维尔天才少年学校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.18,0:27:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有事吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.38,0:27:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这学校怎么了\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, what happened to the School?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.45,0:27:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关闭很多年了\N{\rDefault Eng}School has been shut for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.43,0:27:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是家长吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.89,0:27:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不是\N{\rDefault Eng}Sure as I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.45,0:27:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你哪位  -我是汉克\N{\rDefault Eng}- Who are you? - I'm Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.78,0:27:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉克·麦考伊  现在照料这房子\N{\rDefault Eng}Hank Maccoy, look after the house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.33,0:27:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是野兽\N{\rDefault Eng}You are Beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你  看来是大器晚成啊\N{\rDefault Eng}Look at you, guess you are a late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.85,0:27:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.69,0:27:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回吧\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm gonna have to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-教授呢  -这里没有教授\N{\rDefault Eng}- Where is the professor? - There is no professor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.21,0:27:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人瘦力气倒挺大\N{\rDefault Eng}You're pretty strong for a scrawny kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.17,0:27:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定现在体内没有个小野兽吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Come on, you sure there is no a little Beast in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.09,0:27:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了吧  野兽  -他不在这儿\N{\rDefault Eng}- Come on, Beast. - He is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.74,0:27:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让开  野兽  -不\N{\rDefault Eng}- Come on, Beasty. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.62,0:27:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了学校已经关闭  请你离开\N{\rDefault Eng}I said, the school is closed. You need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.55,0:27:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得见教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Not until I see the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.06,0:27:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿没有教授  听不懂吗\N{\rDefault Eng}There is no professor here. I told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.61,0:28:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  我俩以后会成为好兄弟\N{\rDefault Eng}Look, kid. You and I are gonna be good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.84,0:28:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你现在还不知道\N{\rDefault Eng}You just don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.02,0:28:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.88,0:28:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.40,0:28:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉克  发生什么事了\N{\rDefault Eng}Hank, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.09,0:28:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-教授  -请别这么称呼我\N{\rDefault Eng}-Professor. -Please do not call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.58,0:28:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识这人吗\N{\rDefault Eng}What, you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.02,0:28:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点眼熟\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, he looks slightly familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快从吊灯上下来  汉克\N{\rDefault Eng}Get off the bloody chandelier, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.75,0:28:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能走路\N{\rDefault Eng}You can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.94,0:28:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有洞察力\N{\rDefault Eng}You're a perceptive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.29,0:28:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但埃里克说...\N{\rDefault Eng}I thought Erik...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.17,0:28:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有洞察力\N{\rDefault Eng}which makes it slightly pathetic
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.22,0:28:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没看见大门口的告示\N{\rDefault Eng}that you managed to miss our sign on the way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.35,0:28:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是私人宅邸  朋友\N{\rDefault Eng}This is private property my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.98,0:28:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得让他送你离开\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm gonna have to ask him to ask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:29:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  恕难从命\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, I'm afraid I can't do that because...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.73,0:29:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人派我来找你的\N{\rDefault Eng}Because I was sent here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.05,0:29:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管谁派你来的  告诉他我没空\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, tell whoever it was that sent you that I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不好办\N{\rDefault Eng}This gonna be a little tricky,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.22,0:29:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为派我来的人  就是你自己\N{\rDefault Eng}because the person who sent me was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.71,0:29:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -50年后的你\N{\rDefault Eng}- What? - About 50 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.19,0:29:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50年后  你是说未来的50年后吗\N{\rDefault Eng}50 years from now, like in the future 50 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.08,0:29:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-未来的我把你派来的  -没错\N{\rDefault Eng}- I sent you from the future. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.74,0:29:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚你妈的\N{\rDefault Eng}Piss off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.10,0:29:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的超能力还在  就会明白这是实话\N{\rDefault Eng}If you had your powers, you'd know I was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.69,0:29:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我失去了我的...\N{\rDefault Eng}How do you know I don't have my...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.80,0:29:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是谁\N{\rDefault Eng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.74,0:29:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经告诉你了\N{\rDefault Eng}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.34,0:29:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中情局的人吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You are CIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.40,0:29:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rDefault Eng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.90,0:29:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在监视我\N{\rDefault Eng}You were watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.80,0:29:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}I know you, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.80,0:29:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我是相识多年的好友\N{\rDefault Eng}We've been friends for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.11,0:29:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你9岁时发现了自己有超能力\N{\rDefault Eng}I know your powers came when you were 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.72,0:29:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始你以为自己疯了\N{\rDefault Eng}I know you thought, you were going crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子里声音响个不停\N{\rDefault Eng}when it started, all the voices in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.05,0:29:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到12岁那年\N{\rDefault Eng}and it wasn't until you were 12 that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.74,0:29:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才明白  那些原来是别人脑子里的想法\N{\rDefault Eng}you realized all the voices were in everyone else's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.38,0:29:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要我继续说吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Do you want me to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.75,0:29:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我从没和人提过\N{\rDefault Eng}I never told anyone that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.14,0:30:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时没有  但你以后会说的\N{\rDefault Eng}Not yet no, but, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.25,0:30:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你引起我的兴趣了  找我什么事\N{\rDefault Eng}Alright you've picked my interest, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.58,0:30:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得阻止瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}We have to stop Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.00,0:30:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\rDefault Eng}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.86,0:30:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你的帮助\N{\rDefault Eng}We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.93,0:30:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我该醒醒了\N{\rDefault Eng}Think I'd like to wake up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.23,0:30:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟这事有什么关系\N{\rDefault Eng}What does she have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.25,0:30:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说他们得到了瑞雯的能力  然后呢\N{\rDefault Eng}So, you're saying that they took Raven's power and what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它制成了武器吗\N{\rDefault Eng}They weaponized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.13,0:30:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rDefault Eng}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.83,0:30:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很特别\N{\rDefault Eng}She is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.53,0:30:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初  哨兵只以变种人为目标\N{\rDefault Eng}In the beginning, the sentinels were just targeting mutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.73,0:30:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来  他们开始识别非变种人的基因\N{\rDefault Eng}Then they began to identify the genetics in non-mutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.70,0:30:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有变种后代的普通人也被盯上了\N{\rDefault Eng}Who would eventually have mutant children or grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多普通人试图支援我们  却惨遭屠杀\N{\rDefault Eng}Many of the humans tried to help us, it was a slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.04,0:31:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下最邪恶的人类掌权\N{\rDefault Eng}Leaving only the worst of humanity in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.30,0:31:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经历过许多战争\N{\rDefault Eng}I've been in a lot of wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.06,0:31:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可都没有这次可怕\N{\rDefault Eng}I've never seen anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.00,0:31:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆由她而起\N{\rDefault Eng}And it all starts with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.50,0:31:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是...\N{\rDefault Eng}Let's just say that for the sake of,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.97,0:31:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我相信你  也想帮你\N{\rDefault Eng}the sake that I choose to believe you, that I choose to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.04,0:31:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可瑞雯不会听我的\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven won't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.96,0:31:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的心和灵魂  都属于另一个人了\N{\rDefault Eng}No, her heart and soul belongs to someone else now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.40,0:31:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rDefault Eng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.22,0:31:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们还需要万磁王\N{\rDefault Eng}That's why we gonna need Magneto, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.41,0:31:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.40,0:31:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他被关在哪吧\N{\rDefault Eng}You do know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.89,0:31:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.76,0:31:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是咎由自取\N{\rDefault Eng}He's where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.28,0:31:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么一走了之吗\N{\rDefault Eng}So that's it, you're just gonna walk out?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点不错  果然有洞察力\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh, top marks, like I said, you are perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.43,0:31:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识的教授  对那些迷途的孩子\N{\rDefault Eng}The professor I know would never turn his back
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.17,0:31:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会一走了之\N{\rDefault Eng}on someone who lost their path.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.47,0:31:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他爱的人  更加不会\N{\rDefault Eng}Especially someone he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.04,0:32:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像想起来你是谁了\N{\rDefault Eng}You know, I think I do remember you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.76,0:32:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前  我们曾向你求助\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, we came to you a long time ago seeking your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.60,0:32:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把当时你说的话  再还给你\N{\rDefault Eng}And I'm gonna say to you what you said to us then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.75,0:32:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚你妈的\N{\rDefault Eng}Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.81,0:32:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个孬种给我听好  我经历过很多\N{\rDefault Eng}Listen to me you little shit, I've come a long way,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.82,0:32:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也目睹过无数人死去  \N{\rDefault Eng}and I watched a lot of people die,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.31,0:32:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善良的人们  亲朋好友\N{\rDefault Eng}good people, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.63,0:32:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你要自艾自怜  毫无作为\N{\rDefault Eng}if you're gonna wallow in self pity and do nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.95,0:32:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也会经历同样的悲剧  明白吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Then you're gonna watch the same thing, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.48,0:32:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正人迟早都要死的\N{\rDefault Eng}We all have to die some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.59,0:32:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你了  这里没有教授\N{\rDefault Eng}I told you, there is no professor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.32,0:32:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.26,0:32:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他失去了一切  \N{\rDefault Eng}He lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.28,0:32:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克  瑞雯  他的双腿\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik, Raven, his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.85,0:32:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他修建了学校  实验室  这整个地方\N{\rDefault Eng}He built the school, the labs, this whole place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:33:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎知一个学期之后\N{\rDefault Eng}And just after the first semester,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.91,0:33:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越战形势越来越糟糕\N{\rDefault Eng}the war in Vietnam got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.58,0:33:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多教师学生都应征入伍\N{\rDefault Eng}Many of the teachers and students were drafted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.26,0:33:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这击垮了他\N{\rDefault Eng}It broke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.31,0:33:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把自己封闭了起来\N{\rDefault Eng}He retreated into himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.75,0:33:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮他做点什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I wanted to help do something so..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.23,0:33:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我研究出了治疗他脊椎的血清剂\N{\rDefault Eng}So I designed a serum to treat his spine,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,源自我控制自己异变的配方\N{\rDefault Eng}Derived from the same formula that helps me control my mutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.67,0:33:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的剂量  刚好能制衡异变\N{\rDefault Eng}I take just enough to keep myself balanced but,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.96,0:33:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他用的太多了\N{\rDefault Eng}he takes too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.87,0:33:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试过给他减量  但他无法忍受那痛苦\N{\rDefault Eng}I tried easing him back but he just couldn't bear the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.92,0:33:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子里的那些声音\N{\rDefault Eng}The voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.80,0:33:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用药之后  他又能走路了\N{\rDefault Eng}The treatment gives him his legs but,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.03,0:33:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不够\N{\rDefault Eng}it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.90,0:33:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他\N{\rDefault Eng}He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.76,0:33:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的失去太多了\N{\rDefault Eng}He's just lost too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.65,0:34:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不怕我吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You're not scare to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直相信世上不可能只有我一个\N{\rDefault Eng}I always believed I couldn't be the only one in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫查尔斯·泽维尔\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles Xavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.92,0:34:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.64,0:34:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饿了吗  你一个人吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You're hungry and alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.74,0:34:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃什么随便拿\N{\rDefault Eng}Take whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.20,0:34:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有很多食物  你用不着偷\N{\rDefault Eng}We got lots of food, you don't have to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.15,0:34:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后再也不用偷了\N{\rDefault Eng}In fact, you never have to steal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.20,0:34:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rDefault Eng}And that's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.78,0:34:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你找到她\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll help you get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.46,0:34:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为那些关于未来的鬼话  是为了她\N{\rDefault Eng}Not for any of your future shots but for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.86,0:34:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rDefault Eng}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.15,0:34:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话先说在前头  你不了解埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm telling you this, you do not know Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.55,0:34:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人是个魔鬼  杀人犯\N{\rDefault Eng}The man is a monster. A murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.49,0:34:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你能劝瑞雯改变主意\N{\rDefault Eng}You think you can convince Raven to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.14,0:34:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她劝回家\N{\rDefault Eng}To come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.81,0:34:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rDefault Eng}Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.07,0:34:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你凭什么觉得你能改变他\N{\rDefault Eng}But what makes you think you can change him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.88,0:34:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是你和埃里克一起派我回来的\N{\rDefault Eng}Because you and Erik sent me here back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.31,0:35:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关押他的房间\N{\rDefault Eng}The room they're holding him in was built
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.97,0:35:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建于二战钢铁匮乏时期\N{\rDefault Eng}during the 2nd World War when there was a shortage of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地基是纯水泥沙石  不掺杂一点金属\N{\rDefault Eng}So the foundation is pure concrete and sand, no metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.92,0:35:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被关在地下一百层\N{\rDefault Eng}And he's being held a 100 floors beneath
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.41,0:35:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整栋大楼看守密不透风\N{\rDefault Eng}the most heavily guarded building on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.95,0:35:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么被关\N{\rDefault Eng}Why is he in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.95,0:35:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没告诉你吗\N{\rDefault Eng}What, he forgot to mention?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.31,0:35:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀肯尼迪\N{\rDefault Eng}JFK.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.90,0:35:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他杀的\N{\rDefault Eng}He killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.22,0:35:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎么解释\N{\rDefault Eng}What else would explain
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.02,0:35:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹神奇地在半空变轨了呢\N{\rDefault Eng}the bullet miraculously curving through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.35,0:35:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克可是玩枪老手\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik's always had a way with guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.81,0:35:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定还要把他弄出来吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you sure you want to carry on with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.39,0:35:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你提的计划  不是我\N{\rDefault Eng}This is your plan, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.14,0:35:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没人能帮我们进去  还得出来\N{\rDefault Eng}We don't have any resources to get us in, or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.40,0:35:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我和汉克\N{\rDefault Eng}It's just me and Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.28,0:35:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识个人\N{\rDefault Eng}I know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.85,0:35:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该还是少年  住在华盛顿特区附近\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, he'd be a young man now grew up outside of DC
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.82,0:35:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能上天入地\N{\rDefault Eng}He could get into anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不知道要怎么找到他\N{\rDefault Eng}just don't know how the hell we're gonna find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.53,0:35:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器是不能用了\N{\rDefault Eng}I guess ceribro is out of the question
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.78,0:35:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在电话簿上找\N{\rDefault Eng}We have a phone book.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.22,0:36:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不是准备出行吗  先生\N{\rDefault Eng}I thought you'd be getting ready for your trip, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.68,0:36:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来拿些文件\N{\rDefault Eng}I just came to grab couple of files.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.78,0:36:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新围巾吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Is that a new scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.43,0:36:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好看的\N{\rDefault Eng}It's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.40,0:36:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rDefault Eng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.55,0:37:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frx352\fry22\frz3.533\move(213,57,215,177,0,440)\c&H281A00&}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\fad(330,220)}尸检报告
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.05,0:37:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特拉斯克博士\N{\rDefault Eng}Dr. Trask.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.01,0:37:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rDefault Eng}One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.43,0:37:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴黎会议新增了一些出席人员\N{\rDefault Eng}We added some names to the Paris meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.45,0:37:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rDefault Eng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.77,0:38:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不舒服吗  先生\N{\rDefault Eng}Is there something wrong, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.12,0:38:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rDefault Eng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.61,0:38:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\rDefault Eng}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把日程表打一份给我好吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Would you mind typing up my itinerary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.92,0:38:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想有任何遗漏\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't wanna miss anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.72,0:38:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这  就这  停车\N{\rDefault Eng}Here, here, here. Just stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.69,0:38:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  知道了\N{\rDefault Eng}Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.87,0:38:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我开车  别太得意\N{\rDefault Eng}Next time I'll drive. Don't get use to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.50,0:38:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,41)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}马克西莫夫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又犯什么事了\N{\rDefault Eng}What has he done now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.63,0:38:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿了多少  我直接写支票\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll just write you a check for whatever he took.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.46,0:38:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只想跟他谈谈\N{\rDefault Eng}We just need talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.31,0:38:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮特  警察先生又来了\N{\rDefault Eng}Peter, the cops are here, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.76,0:39:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我干的\N{\rDefault Eng}Guess what, I didn't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.24,0:39:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一天都待在家里\N{\rDefault Eng}I've been here all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.62,0:39:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  皮特  我们不是警察\N{\rDefault Eng}Just relax Peter, we are not cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.52,0:39:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是\N{\rDefault Eng}Of course you're not cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.17,0:39:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是警察就不会租车来了\N{\rDefault Eng}if you were cops you wouldn't drive a rental car
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们是租的车\N{\rDefault Eng}How'd you know we got a rental car?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.96,0:39:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了你们的登记记录\N{\rDefault Eng}I checked your registration
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.77,0:39:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你们走进来的时候\N{\rDefault Eng}when you were walking through the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.22,0:39:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你们还在走\N{\rDefault Eng}I also had some time to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.06,0:39:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就顺便看了租车协议  \N{\rDefault Eng}so I went through your rental agreements,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.21,0:39:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现你们是外地人\N{\rDefault Eng}saw you were from out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.50,0:39:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦调查局的吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.39,0:39:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是  这个天才少年学校是什么地方\N{\rDefault Eng}No, you're not cops, hey what's up with this gifted youngster's place
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张旧名片而已\N{\rDefault Eng}That's an old card.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.34,0:39:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真厉害\N{\rDefault Eng}He is fascinating,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.35,0:39:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个混球\N{\rDefault Eng}He is a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.48,0:39:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瞬间移动吗\N{\rDefault Eng}What, a teleporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.47,0:39:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  就是速度快\N{\rDefault Eng}No, He's just fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.82,0:39:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识他的时候  他可没这么年轻\N{\rDefault Eng}When I know him he wasn't so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻  是你们老吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Young? You're just old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.05,0:39:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不怕向人展示你的超能力吗\N{\rDefault Eng}So you're not afraid to show your powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.12,0:39:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力  什么东西  说什么呢\N{\rDefault Eng}Power? What power? What you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.47,0:39:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到什么不寻常的事了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You see some strange here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.20,0:39:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出去也没人会相信\N{\rDefault Eng}Nothing anybody would believe if you told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.27,0:39:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人  找我干什么\N{\rDefault Eng}So who are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.00,0:39:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你帮个忙  皮特\N{\rDefault Eng}We need your help, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.06,0:39:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么忙\N{\rDefault Eng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.91,0:39:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入一座严防死守的大楼\N{\rDefault Eng}Break into a highly secured facility
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.38,0:39:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救个人出来\N{\rDefault Eng}and get someone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.82,0:39:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Prison break?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.59,0:39:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是违法的\N{\rDefault Eng}That's illegal, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.04,0:40:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住了才算违法\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, only if you get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.01,0:40:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啥好处\N{\rDefault Eng}What's there in for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.13,0:40:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个偷盗狂  我们要潜入的是五角大楼\N{\rDefault Eng}You, the kleptomaniac, get to break into the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.59,0:40:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么相信你们\N{\rDefault Eng}How do I know I can trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.17,0:40:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是一类人\N{\rDefault Eng}Because we are just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.02,0:40:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他瞧瞧\N{\rDefault Eng}Show him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.04,0:40:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺酷的  就是有点恶心\N{\rDefault Eng}It's cool, just disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.08,0:40:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,41)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}国防部
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.87,0:40:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五角大楼建于1943年  \N{\rDefault Eng}Built in 1943,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.40,0:40:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是世界最大的办公楼\N{\rDefault Eng}the Pentagon is the world largest office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.05,0:40:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本部雇军两万五千人\N{\rDefault Eng}Housing more than 25000 military employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.69,0:40:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占地超过六百万平方英尺\N{\rDefault Eng}stretched over 6 million square feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.72,0:40:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厕所在哪  我要尿尿\N{\rDefault Eng}Where is the bathroom? I need to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.62,0:40:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位非常幸运  我们有...\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, lucky for you, you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.87,0:41:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rDefault Eng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.29,0:41:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz336.306\org(102,117)\pos(136,136)\frx14\fry40}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HD0D3BB&}由此往前\N不得使用任何金属
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.33,0:41:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监控都变成电视节目了  怎么回事\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, we're getting broadcast signal down here.What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.72,0:41:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  快叫维修部的人来\N{\rDefault Eng}Damn it! Call the maintenance, get them down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.34,0:42:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz334.601\frx34\fry8\org(257,79)\pos(231,114)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H282206&}当心玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.03,0:43:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...日本帝国主义\N{\rDefault Eng}....from a Japanese empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.99,0:43:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战火持续了一个月\N{\rDefault Eng}This month long battle
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.34,0:43:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二战中非常残酷的几场交战便在其中\N{\rDefault Eng}included some of the fearsome fighting during World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.74,0:44:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3秒后门会打开\N{\rDefault Eng}In 3 seconds those doors are going to open,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.54,0:44:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20个守卫已经准备好射杀我们\N{\rDefault Eng}and 20 guards will be here to shoot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.79,0:44:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  正等着呢\N{\rDefault Eng}I know, that's what I'm waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.39,0:44:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.53,0:44:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护好你的脖子  防止颈椎扭伤\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm holding your neck so you won't get whip-lash
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.16,0:44:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.49,0:44:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颈椎  扭伤\N{\rDefault Eng}Whip...la..sh
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.28,0:44:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\rDefault Eng}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.66,0:44:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很厉害  没事的\N{\rDefault Eng}You're good. It'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.21,0:44:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑起来就这样\N{\rDefault Eng}It happens when I run.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.43,0:44:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定犯了很严重的事\N{\rDefault Eng}Must have done something pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.72,0:44:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么啊  哥们儿\N{\rDefault Eng}What're you do, man? What you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.65,0:44:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了什么坏事  被关到这鬼地方\N{\rDefault Eng}What're you do? Why would they have you in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.82,0:44:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺杀总统\N{\rDefault Eng}For killing the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.42,0:44:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的罪过就是为我们的同胞而战\N{\rDefault Eng}Anything I'm guilty of is fighting for people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.98,0:45:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会空手道吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You take Karate? You know Karate, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.88,0:45:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂空手道\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't know Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.10,0:45:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道疯子\N{\rDefault Eng}But I know crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.38,0:45:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位男女老少  现在是红色警戒\N{\rDefault Eng}Ladies and gentlemen, boys and girls, this is a code red situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.47,0:45:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得疏散整个楼层\N{\rDefault Eng}We are evacuating the entire floor so that we,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.25,0:45:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我和同事才能截住犯人\N{\rDefault Eng}my associate and I can secure the prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.45,0:45:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人\N{\rDefault Eng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.27,0:45:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是消防  检疫  防爆特别行动...\N{\rDefault Eng}We are special operations CB, FE, CIED...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.86,0:45:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  可能你们刚才没听见我说\N{\rDefault Eng}Look, perhaps you didn't hear me what first I spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.30,0:45:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们必须明白\N{\rDefault Eng}But it's imperative
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里已经绝对封锁了\N{\rDefault Eng}that you understand we're in complete lock down situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.03,0:45:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得去三楼...\N{\rDefault Eng}We have to get into the 3rd floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.98,0:45:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  抱歉  你说完了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh, I'm sorry, were you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.98,0:45:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说你可以控制金属\N{\rDefault Eng}They told me you can control the metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.25,0:45:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他们"\N{\rDefault Eng}"They"?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.33,0:45:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈上过一个能控制金属的人\N{\rDefault Eng}You know my mom once knew a guy who could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.20,0:45:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我这人不太喜欢动粗\N{\rDefault Eng}Sorry, I'm just not very good with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.21,0:46:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.22,0:46:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  老朋友\N{\rDefault Eng}Good to see you too, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.31,0:46:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你又能走了  -可不是你的功劳\N{\rDefault Eng}- And walking? - No thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.48,0:46:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么也没想到你会来\N{\rDefault Eng}You're the last person in the world I expected to see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.18,0:46:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  要不是逼不得已我也不会来\N{\rDefault Eng}Believe me, I wouldn't be here if I didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.52,0:46:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救你出去  你就得听我的\N{\rDefault Eng}If we get you out of here, we do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.78,0:46:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许杀人\N{\rDefault Eng}No killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.14,0:46:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有头盔\N{\rDefault Eng}No helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.73,0:46:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算想违抗你也做不到啊\N{\rDefault Eng}I couldn't disobey you even if I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.74,0:46:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再进入你脑子里了\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm never getting inside of that head again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.80,0:46:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你答应我  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}I need your word, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.03,0:46:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\rDefault Eng}No body move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.61,0:46:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  不许动\N{\rDefault Eng}Hold it, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.63,0:46:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-查尔斯  -不许动\N{\rDefault Eng}- Charles. - Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.41,0:46:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来  否则我们就开枪了\N{\rDefault Eng}Hands up or we'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.80,0:46:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-定住他们  查尔斯  -我不行\N{\rDefault Eng}- Freeze them, Charles. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.41,0:46:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\rDefault Eng}Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.36,0:46:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\rDefault Eng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.30,0:47:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能把时间留住\N{\rDefault Eng}If I could save time in a bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.72,0:47:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我首先要做的\N{\rDefault Eng}The first thing that I like to do
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.70,0:47:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是留住每一天\N{\rDefault Eng}is to save every day 'til eternity passes away
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.33,0:47:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好与你一起分享\N{\rDefault Eng}Just to spend them with you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.59,0:47:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果今天不会消逝\N{\rDefault Eng}If I could make days last forever
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.86,0:47:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能心想事成\N{\rDefault Eng}If words could make wishes come true
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.02,0:47:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会珍藏每一天\N{\rDefault Eng}I'd save every day like a treasure and then
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好与你一起分享\N{\rDefault Eng}Again, I would spend them with you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.76,0:47:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是做自己喜欢的事\N{\rDefault Eng}But there never seems to be enough time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.78,0:47:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间永远都不够用\N{\rDefault Eng}To do the things you want to do once you find them
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.80,0:48:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这世上活了好久\N{\rDefault Eng}I've looked around enough to know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.69,0:48:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想与你分享时光\N{\rDefault Eng}That you're the one I want to go through time with
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.66,0:48:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  小子\N{\rDefault Eng}Thanks, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.85,0:48:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮特  这次真的非常感谢你\N{\rDefault Eng}Peter, thank you very very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.17,0:48:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重\N{\rDefault Eng}You take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.06,0:48:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在驾驶舱看到了你们的飞行计划\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, I saw your flight plan in the cockpit,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.45,0:49:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去巴黎干嘛\N{\rDefault Eng}why you going to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.54,0:49:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\org(204,157)\pos(175,129)\frx18\fry2\frz341.541}{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs30\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H08070A&}和平协定将在巴黎签署
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.17,0:49:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是金属爪子看你还怎么玩\N{\rDefault Eng}Imagine if they were metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.40,0:49:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我个忙  把车还回去\N{\rDefault Eng}Do me a favor and return it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.81,0:49:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  -皮特...\N{\rDefault Eng}- Okay - Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.02,0:49:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点开\N{\rDefault Eng}Take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.57,0:49:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么找上你的\N{\rDefault Eng}Where did they dig you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.56,0:49:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来你可能不信  不过\N{\rDefault Eng}You're gonna find this hard to believe, but ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.14,0:49:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你让我来的\N{\rDefault Eng}You sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.03,0:49:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}You and Charles,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.30,0:49:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的你们\N{\rDefault Eng}from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.41,0:49:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么失去能力的\N{\rDefault Eng}How did you lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.67,0:50:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗脊柱的药物限制了我的DNA\N{\rDefault Eng}The treatment for my spine fixed my DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.75,0:50:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你牺牲自己的能力就为了能走路\N{\rDefault Eng}You sacrificed your powers so you could walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.19,0:50:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我牺牲自己的能力是为了...\N{\rDefault Eng}I sacrificed my powers so that I could sl...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.76,0:50:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又知道什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.87,0:50:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也失去了很多东西\N{\rDefault Eng}I've lost my fair share.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.23,0:50:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别委屈了  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Hah. Dry your eyes, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.78,0:50:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这无法为你所做的一切开脱\N{\rDefault Eng}It doesn't justify what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.47,0:50:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不知道我做了什么\N{\rDefault Eng}You've no idea what I have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.13,0:50:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你夺走了我最珍贵的东西\N{\rDefault Eng}I know that you took the things that mean most to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.48,0:50:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你当初就该更努力地保护它们\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, maybe you should have fought harder for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.24,0:50:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想打架吗  埃里克  那我们就打一架\N{\rDefault Eng}Do you want to fight, Erik? I'll give you a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.04,0:50:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让他来  -你抛弃了我\N{\rDefault Eng}- Let him come. - You abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.78,0:50:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你夺走了她  然后抛弃了我\N{\rDefault Eng}You took her away and you abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.29,0:50:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使\N{\rDefault Eng}Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.08,0:50:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿撒佐\N{\rDefault Eng}Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.08,0:50:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾玛\N{\rDefault Eng}Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.03,0:50:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海妖\N{\rDefault Eng}Banshee.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.49,0:50:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些变种兄弟姐妹都死了\N{\rDefault Eng}Mutant brothers and sisters all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.49,0:50:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有无数其他同胞\N{\rDefault Eng}Countless others...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.86,0:50:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...被抓去做实验  被屠杀\N{\rDefault Eng}...experimented on, butchered.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.05,0:50:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.69,0:50:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候你在哪儿  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Where were you, Charles?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.91,0:50:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本该保护他们免受残害\N{\rDefault Eng}We were supposed to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.40,0:51:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你的兄弟姐妹需要你时  你在哪儿\N{\rDefault Eng}Where were you your own people needed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.94,0:51:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你藏起来了\N{\rDefault Eng}Hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.35,0:51:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和汉克  自欺欺人不敢面对真实的自己\N{\rDefault Eng}You and Hank, pretending you were something you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.01,0:51:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.07,0:51:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你抛弃了大家\N{\rDefault Eng}You abandoned us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.69,0:51:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你一直都这么混蛋\N{\rDefault Eng}So you were always an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.43,0:51:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我们在未来是好兄弟\N{\rDefault Eng}I take it we're best buddies in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.76,0:51:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我花了很多年想干掉你  兄弟\N{\rDefault Eng}I spent a lot of years trying to bring you down, bub.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.43,0:51:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果怎样\N{\rDefault Eng}How is that work out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.28,0:51:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样\N{\rDefault Eng}You're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.18,0:51:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是个幸存者\N{\rDefault Eng}You're a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.17,0:51:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这儿收拾一下行吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You wanna pick all that shit up?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.30,0:52:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20\b0\pos(192,215)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,863,\alpha0)\t(2025,2526,\alpha&HFF&)}巴   黎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.05,0:52:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军  慢点喝吧\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}General, maybe you should slow down,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.39,0:52:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可是个大日子\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we have a big day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.63,0:52:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是来庆祝的  上尉\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're celebrating, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.51,0:52:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜仗可不是天天有的\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not every day you win a war,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.12,0:52:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况是战胜了美国鬼子\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}let alone against the American devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.36,0:52:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要再来一瓶\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm getting another bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.34,0:52:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.59,0:52:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我自己不小心\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm pretty sure it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.98,0:52:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你会越南语  -我是个翻译\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- You speak Vietnamese. - I'm an interpreter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.60,0:52:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好几种语言\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I speak many tongues.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.87,0:53:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再请你喝一杯\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me buy you another drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.29,0:53:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你还有其他男伴\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}unless you're here with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.16,0:53:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.81,0:53:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要参加明天的峰会吗\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're going to the summit tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.65,0:53:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小美人对政治感兴趣\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The pretty girl interested in politics...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.27,0:53:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不能光看外表啊\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Looks can be deceiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.68,0:53:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是哦\N{\fe238}{\fn方正大黑简体}{\fs14}{\b1}{\c&H65D8E2&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.00,0:53:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看  宝贝\N{\rDefault Eng}Show me more, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.89,0:53:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服  脱了\N{\rDefault Eng}Clothes...off.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.17,0:54:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  宝贝\N{\rDefault Eng}What's the matter, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.73,0:54:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿着衣服就不美吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You don't think I look pretty like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.52,0:54:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一盘吗  好久没下了\N{\rDefault Eng}Fancy a game? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.20,0:54:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没心情下棋\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm not in the mood for games exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.04,0:55:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年都没好好喝一口了\N{\rDefault Eng}Haven't had a real sip in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.71,0:55:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统不是我杀的\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't kill the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.96,0:55:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹拐弯了  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}The bullet curved, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.38,0:55:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我想救他\N{\rDefault Eng}Because I was trying to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.38,0:55:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没救成我就被拿下了\N{\rDefault Eng}They took me out before I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.89,0:55:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你为什么要救他  -因为他是我们的一员\N{\rDefault Eng}- Why would you trying to save him? - Because he was one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.83,0:55:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定觉得我蠢透了\N{\rDefault Eng}You must think me so foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.09,0:55:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总说他们会找上我们\N{\rDefault Eng}You've always said they would come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.04,0:55:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过他们会利用瑞雯的DNA\N{\rDefault Eng}I never imagined they would use Raven's DNA to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.50,0:55:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最后一次见她是什么时候\N{\rDefault Eng}When did you last see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.50,0:56:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动身去达拉斯的那天\N{\rDefault Eng}The day I left to Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.26,0:56:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么样\N{\rDefault Eng}And how was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.59,0:56:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强\N{\rDefault Eng}Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.39,0:56:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有冲劲\N{\rDefault Eng}Driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.87,0:56:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-忠诚  -我是问\N{\rDefault Eng}- Loyal. - How...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.89,0:56:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她过得怎么样\N{\rDefault Eng}How was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.30,0:56:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她...\N{\rDefault Eng}She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.37,0:56:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解她对你为何如此重要\N{\rDefault Eng}I could see why she meant so much to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.41,0:56:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该为她感到自豪  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}You should be proud of her, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.63,0:56:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她是在为我们的事业而战  -你的事业\N{\rDefault Eng}- She is out there fighting for our cause. - Your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.97,0:56:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我养大的那个女孩不会杀人\N{\rDefault Eng}The girl I raised, she was not capable of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.06,0:56:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没养她  你只是和她一起长大\N{\rDefault Eng}You didn't raise her, you grew up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.42,0:56:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不能永远做个小女孩  所以她离开了你\N{\rDefault Eng}She couldn't stay a little girl forever that's why she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.71,0:56:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她离开我是因为你干扰了她的思想\N{\rDefault Eng}She left because you got inside her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.59,0:56:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这个能力\N{\rDefault Eng}That's not my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.46,0:56:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是她的选择\N{\rDefault Eng}She made a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.94,0:56:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们现在知道那选择会有什么结局了\N{\rDefault Eng}But now we know where that choice leads, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.18,0:57:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会去刺杀特拉斯克  他们会抓住她\N{\rDefault Eng}She's going to murder Trask, they're going to capture her,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.30,0:57:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们会被赶尽杀绝\N{\rDefault Eng}and then they're going to wipe us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.77,0:57:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们先找到她就不会\N{\rDefault Eng}Not if we get to her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.83,0:57:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们明天能扭转这一切就不会\N{\rDefault Eng}Not if we change history tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.56,0:57:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm sorry, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.67,0:57:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为所有这一切  真的对不起\N{\rDefault Eng}For what happened, I truly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.00,0:57:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有一阵子没玩了\N{\rDefault Eng}It's been a while since I played.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.42,0:57:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让着你的\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.72,0:57:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下算是公平点了吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Might finally get a fair fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.86,0:57:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先下\N{\rDefault Eng}You make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.00,0:57:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各国的外交官员今天齐聚于此\N{\rDefault Eng}The diplomats from all around the world arriving here today at the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.04,0:57:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇家酒店\N{\rDefault Eng}hotel Royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.45,0:58:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是具有历史意义的一天\N{\rDefault Eng}It's a historic day as the official ending of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.98,0:58:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国对越南的军事干预将正式结束\N{\rDefault Eng}the united states fierce involvement in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.32,0:58:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在到达的是越南外交部长\N{\rDefault Eng}There's the south Vietnamese foreign minister
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.28,0:58:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及随行官员\N{\rDefault Eng}with other south Vietnamese dignitaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.29,0:58:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,峰会还有一个小时才开始\N{\rDefault Eng}The summit doesn't begin for another hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.66,0:58:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为您的贵客们在楼上准备了一个房间\N{\rDefault Eng}The hotel has arranged a private room upstairs for your special guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.89,0:58:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间足够了\N{\rDefault Eng}That'll be plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.05,0:58:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好  各位下午好\N{\rDefault Eng}Good afternoon, everyone, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.11,0:58:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位出席\N{\rDefault Eng}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.34,0:58:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先祝贺各位取得胜利\N{\rDefault Eng}Congratulations on winning this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.29,0:58:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道各位都急着下楼\N{\rDefault Eng}Now I know you all have
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.65,0:58:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握手合影  应付场面\N{\rDefault Eng}hands to shake and photos to take downstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.32,0:58:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就长话短说了\N{\rDefault Eng}so I will get right to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.59,0:58:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们有一个新敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}There is a new enemy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.23,0:58:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个用武器无法阻止的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}An enemy that will render your arsenals useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.68,0:58:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个能令国防瘫痪的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}your armies powerless and your nations defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.87,0:58:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们需要一种新武器来赢得这场战争\N{\rDefault Eng}You'll need a new weapon for this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.05,0:58:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将其命名为"哨兵"\N{\rDefault Eng}I call them "Sentinels".
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.59,0:59:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取自古时的城堡卫兵\N{\rDefault Eng}Named after the ancient guardians that stood at the gates of the citadel,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.64,0:59:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行能力相当于一架鹞式战斗机\N{\rDefault Eng}they have the aeronautic capabilities of a Harrier Jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.30,0:59:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配备的枪械\N{\rDefault Eng}Armed with guns that can fire off
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.36,0:59:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每分钟可发射2000轮热电陶瓷子弹\N{\rDefault Eng}more than 2000 rounds per minute with thermo-ceramic ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.99,0:59:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有足够的尺寸  威力及速度\N{\rDefault Eng}But size, power, speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.56,0:59:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克希德或波音的飞机也能做到这点\N{\rDefault Eng}you could find that at Lockheed or Boeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.74,0:59:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  "哨兵"的真正特别之处在于\N{\rDefault Eng}No! What makes the sentinels so special
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.59,0:59:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以自动搜索到变种人的X基因\N{\rDefault Eng}is the ability to target the mutant X gene.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.40,0:59:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的基因导向系统\N{\rDefault Eng}The genetic guidance system
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.89,0:59:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以搜寻到半英里外的目标\N{\rDefault Eng}that can lock onto a mark half a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.58,0:59:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且只有确认了目标才会触发\N{\rDefault Eng}And won't trigger unless it has identified the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.83,0:59:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了它  就可以避免连带的人员伤亡\N{\rDefault Eng}With this weapon there'll be no human collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.46,0:59:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我现在打开  它并不会被激活\N{\rDefault Eng}If I turn it on, the system couldn't even activate in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.77,0:59:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非...\N{\rDefault Eng}Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.56,0:59:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}there's a mutant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.47,1:00:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是搞错了\N{\rDefault Eng}There has to be some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.90,1:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的机器从不出错\N{\rDefault Eng}My machines don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.00,1:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.34,1:00:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rDefault Eng}I assure you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.78,1:00:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\rDefault Eng}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.37,1:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  别开枪\N{\rDefault Eng}No, don't shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.68,1:00:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rDefault Eng}I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.35,1:00:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I do not know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.30,1:00:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.56,1:01:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.83,1:01:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.80,1:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.19,1:01:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.33,1:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来找你了  我和埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}We've come for you. Erik and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.13,1:01:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起\N{\rDefault Eng}Together.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.00,1:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到还能再见到你\N{\rDefault Eng}I never thought I could see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.37,1:01:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经许下承诺要保护你\N{\rDefault Eng}I made you a promise long time ago that I would protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.33,1:01:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没做到  我知道...\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't. And I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.02,1:01:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金刚狼\N{\rDefault Eng}Wolverine!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.64,1:01:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你的\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm going to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.79,1:01:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让他们把你带走的\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm going to keep you out of their hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.51,1:01:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.12,1:01:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.35,1:01:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干嘛\N{\rDefault Eng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.01,1:01:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭转我们的未来\N{\rDefault Eng}Securing our future.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.16,1:01:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怪我  魔形女\N{\rDefault Eng}Forgive me, Mystique.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.05,1:01:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活着我们就不会安全\N{\rDefault Eng}As long as you're out there we'll never be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.14,1:01:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.93,1:01:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制他  查尔斯  让他停下\N{\rDefault Eng}Use your power, Charles. Stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.02,1:02:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做不到了\N{\rDefault Eng}He can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.99,1:02:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在挣脱  他的意识在波动\N{\rDefault Eng}He is slipping. He is slipping back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.68,1:02:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他快挣脱我了\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm losing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.48,1:03:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史崔克\N{\rDefault Eng}Stryker!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.07,1:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我们会完成这一切  金刚狼\N{\rDefault Eng}So we will finish what we started Wolverine, oneday.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.51,1:03:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯蒂\N{\rDefault Eng}Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.84,1:03:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制住他\N{\rDefault Eng}Restrain him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.04,1:03:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.23,1:03:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪儿\N{\rDefault Eng}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.36,1:03:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会在这儿\N{\rDefault Eng}How the hell did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.55,1:04:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  你来找的我们\N{\rDefault Eng}What? You came to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.20,1:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是谁  -查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}- Who are you? - Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.16,1:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯·泽维尔\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles Xavier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.30,1:04:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不认识你  -啊 \N{\rDefault Eng}- I do not know you. - Ahh?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.22,1:04:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.25,1:04:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来处理这个\N{\rDefault Eng}Wow, I can deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.34,1:04:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走  去找埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Just go. Stop Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.84,1:04:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.23,1:04:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.35,1:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.57,1:04:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是罗根  他是汉克·麦考伊\N{\rDefault Eng}You are Logan. That's Hank McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.96,1:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是查尔斯·泽维尔\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm Charles Xavier.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.01,1:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这几天一直在一起\N{\rDefault Eng}You spent the last couple of days with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.75,1:04:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嗑药了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You're on Acid?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.13,1:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计嗑的也不是好货\N{\rDefault Eng}Somebody gave you really bad acid.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.68,1:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.08,1:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再坚持一下  我们会撑过去的\N{\rDefault Eng}Just hold on tight, we'll get through this together.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.85,1:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  凯蒂\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh, God! Kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.05,1:05:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她伤得很重\N{\rDefault Eng}She is wounded pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.53,1:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我控制住他了\N{\rDefault Eng}I got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.59,1:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.13,1:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才怎么了\N{\rDefault Eng}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.76,1:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了一个未来将会折磨我的人\N{\rDefault Eng}I just saw someone who's going to bring me a lot of pain someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.72,1:07:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯呢\N{\rDefault Eng}Where is Raven?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.36,1:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑了\N{\rDefault Eng}Gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.24,1:07:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -我们得走了\N{\rDefault Eng}- What? - We have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.72,1:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天  一些不明攻击者的出现\N{\rDefault Eng}Yesterday the Paris Peace Summit
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.29,1:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱了巴黎和平峰会\N{\rDefault Eng}was rocked by the appearance of unidentified assailants.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.46,1:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们此前从未见过这样的人\N{\rDefault Eng}The likes of which the world has never seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.82,1:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大的恐慌席卷了全国  人们都在问\N{\rDefault Eng}Mass hysteria has gripped the nation as people ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.64,1:07:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从哪儿来  他们还会回来吗\N{\rDefault Eng}"Where did they come from? Will they'd be back?",
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.02,1:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有最重要的一点\N{\rDefault Eng}and most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.39,1:07:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是敌是友\N{\rDefault Eng}"Are they friend or foe?".
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.32,1:07:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是本节目通讯记者汤米·艾略特\N{\rDefault Eng}That was "One" correspondent Tommy Elliot
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.71,1:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从昨日巴黎和平峰会现场发回的报道\N{\rDefault Eng}earlier reporting from the Paris Peace Summit yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.38,1:07:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁能告诉我这是怎么回事\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell are we dealing with here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.16,1:07:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把录音关了\N{\rDefault Eng}Off the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.81,1:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前\N{\rDefault Eng}Two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.00,1:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人  埃里克·兰谢尔\N{\rDefault Eng}this man Erik Lehnsherr
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.99,1:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从五角大楼最高警戒牢房逃出来了\N{\rDefault Eng}escaped from a maximum security prison inside the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.02,1:07:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人  曾经是他的同伙\N{\rDefault Eng}We believe that this woman is a former associate of Lehnsherr's.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.71,1:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,62年导弹危机的时候  他们都在古巴\N{\rDefault Eng}They were together in Cuba the day of the crisis in 1962.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.00,1:08:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还和肯尼迪被刺一案有关\N{\rDefault Eng}He was also implicated in Kennedy's assassination.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.99,1:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西又是什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What about that thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.39,1:08:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前还不了解  先生\N{\rDefault Eng}We do not know what that thing is, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.05,1:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上我们对他们全都不了解\N{\rDefault Eng}Actually we really don't know what any of them are.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.46,1:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.28,1:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我们了解\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes, We do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.95,1:08:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}They are mutants.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.73,1:08:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人能够操控金属\N{\rDefault Eng}He has the power to control metal.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.82,1:08:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知你们所有的武器都是金属的\N{\rDefault Eng}Last I checked that's what most of your weapons were made of.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.95,1:08:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她能够变成任何人\N{\rDefault Eng}And she can transform into anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.72,1:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名将军\N{\rDefault Eng}A general.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.71,1:08:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名特工\N{\rDefault Eng}A secret service man.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.71,1:08:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是您  总统阁下\N{\rDefault Eng}Even you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.81,1:08:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她甚至能走进这间办公室下令发射核武器\N{\rDefault Eng}She can walk into this office, and order a nuclear strike,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.54,1:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她愿意\N{\rDefault Eng}if she was in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.51,1:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这还只是他们中的两个\N{\rDefault Eng}And that's only two of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.68,1:08:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有什么对策或者防御措施吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Well, do we have any countermeasures, any defense?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.25,1:08:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的就是这个问题\N{\rDefault Eng}I was waiting for you to ask me that question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.54,1:08:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项目还处在实验阶段  \N{\rDefault Eng}That's an experimental program, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.88,1:08:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是私下进行的\N{\rDefault Eng}Strictly, off the books.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.09,1:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说世界上有这些变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}You're telling me these mutants are out in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.89,1:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们最佳的防御方式是这些大机器人吗\N{\rDefault Eng}and our best defense are these giant metal robots?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.42,1:09:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多变种人看起来跟我们一样\N{\rDefault Eng}Many of the mutants looks like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.02,1:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哨兵能分辨出他们\N{\rDefault Eng}My sentinels can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.52,1:09:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在有八台原型机随时可用\N{\rDefault Eng}I have 8 prototypes ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.93,1:09:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是用太空材料制成的\N{\rDefault Eng}they're built out of a space age polymer,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.77,1:09:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不含金属\N{\rDefault Eng}not an ounce of metal on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.25,1:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做一次展示\N{\rDefault Eng}I wanna make a demonstration,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.75,1:09:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让世界知道我们能保护他们\N{\rDefault Eng}I want the world to know that we can protect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.49,1:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么启动他们\N{\rDefault Eng}What do you need to get these things operational?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.04,1:09:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经向国会申请了拨款\N{\rDefault Eng}I already gave that number to congress
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.94,1:09:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不幸  被否决了\N{\rDefault Eng}unfortunately they elected to shut me down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.80,1:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要启动可能代价会稍微大一点\N{\rDefault Eng}It's going to cost a bit more to turn them on.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.62,1:09:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你所需\N{\rDefault Eng}Whatever you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.28,1:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  如果成功抓住了他们\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh, and one more thing, if we do manage to capture them,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.29,1:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能用她来做研究\N{\rDefault Eng}I would like her for research purposes of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.10,1:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\rDefault Eng}Terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.83,1:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rDefault Eng}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.32,1:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天生那副模样\N{\rDefault Eng}Being born like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.08,1:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.61,1:09:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can you imagine?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.32,1:09:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天对着镜子看到那样一张脸\N{\rDefault Eng}Looking in the mirror and seeing that staring back at you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.81,1:10:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能想象\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.85,1:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得她是从哪里来的\N{\rDefault Eng}Where do you think she comes from?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.77,1:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有家吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You think she has a family?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.33,1:10:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她有\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.50,1:11:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢动一颗螺丝钉我就把它插进你喉咙\N{\rDefault Eng}If I see so much as a screw move I'll jam this into your throat.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.46,1:11:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么找到我的\N{\rDefault Eng}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.00,1:11:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我教得很好\N{\rDefault Eng}You taught me well.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.82,1:11:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很久没这么亲近了\N{\rDefault Eng}It's been a long time since we were this close.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.67,1:11:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想你\N{\rDefault Eng}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.11,1:11:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想杀我\N{\rDefault Eng}You tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.96,1:11:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样其他人才能活\N{\rDefault Eng}So the rest of us could live.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.69,1:11:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rDefault Eng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.48,1:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到一条来自未来的消息\N{\rDefault Eng}I received a message from the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.47,1:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少骗我\N{\rDefault Eng}Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.83,1:11:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有  也永远不会骗你\N{\rDefault Eng}I never have, I never will.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.86,1:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类用你的血和基因\N{\rDefault Eng}Humans use your blood, your genes,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.90,1:11:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造出了能毁灭我们的武器\N{\rDefault Eng}to create a weapon that wipes us all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.87,1:11:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是做了我觉得能保护我们未来的事\N{\rDefault Eng}I was only doing what I thought necessary to secure our future.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.89,1:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么能阻止我\N{\rDefault Eng}So what's to stop me from
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.05,1:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在杀了你来保护我自己的未来\N{\rDefault Eng}killing you right now and securing my future?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.69,1:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rDefault Eng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.15,1:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无所谓了\N{\rDefault Eng}It doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.06,1:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们得到了你的DNA  \N{\rDefault Eng}They have your DNA,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.58,1:11:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的血滴在了街上\N{\rDefault Eng}your blood was on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.71,1:11:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁的错\N{\rDefault Eng}Whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.77,1:11:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的\N{\rDefault Eng}Mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.01,1:12:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过他们的计划\N{\rDefault Eng}I've seen their plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.04,1:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在制造一种武器\N{\rDefault Eng}They are creating a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.43,1:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他们已经得到了进行下去的关键东西\N{\rDefault Eng}and now they have what they need to take it further.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.80,1:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须行动起来\N{\rDefault Eng}We have to strike now,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.29,1:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁我们还有优势\N{\rDefault Eng}while we still hold the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.94,1:12:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了太多同伴的死亡  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}I've seen too many friends die, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.98,1:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想要战争\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't want a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.72,1:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想找到杀了他们的人\N{\rDefault Eng}I only want the man who murdered them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.37,1:12:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是战争\N{\rDefault Eng}This is a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.76,1:12:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了\N{\rDefault Eng}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.42,1:12:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开这段时间  你迷失了方向吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Did you lose your way when I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.69,1:12:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是查尔斯的瑞雯吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you still Charles's Raven?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.05,1:12:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是魔形女\N{\rDefault Eng}Or are you Mystique?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.86,1:12:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特拉斯克才是敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}Trask is the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.64,1:12:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉一个人远远不够\N{\rDefault Eng}Killing one man isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.01,1:12:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说永远都不够\N{\rDefault Eng}It never was for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.74,1:12:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Good Bye, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.56,1:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\rDefault Eng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.13,1:13:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能走吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can he walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.31,1:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要接受治疗\N{\rDefault Eng}He need his treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.01,1:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉克  我能听到他们说话\N{\rDefault Eng}Hank, I can hear them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.05,1:13:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我能让它停下  我去拿药\N{\rDefault Eng}It's ok, I'll make it stop. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.79,1:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  喂  坚持住\N{\rDefault Eng}Hey, Hey. Pull yourself together
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.19,1:13:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢\N{\rDefault Eng}It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.34,1:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不相信\N{\rDefault Eng}You don't believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.62,1:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\rDefault Eng}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.58,1:13:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不能动\N{\rDefault Eng}As these go,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.54,1:13:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就回来了\N{\rDefault Eng}this comes back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.51,1:13:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全都回来了\N{\rDefault Eng}They all come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.00,1:13:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着\N{\rDefault Eng}Look, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.18,1:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在这里\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.82,1:14:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在外面\N{\rDefault Eng}She's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.39,1:14:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们需要你的帮助  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}But we need your help, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.17,1:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样  我需要的是你\N{\rDefault Eng}Not like this, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.30,1:14:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你的能力\N{\rDefault Eng}We can't find Raven..
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.67,1:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找不到瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}not without your powers.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.25,1:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多加了一点  因为你少打了一针\N{\rDefault Eng}I added a little extra cause you missed a dose.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.13,1:14:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.68,1:15:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉克  帮我个忙\N{\rDefault Eng}Hank, do me a favour.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.49,1:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扶我去书房好吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Would you help me to my study please?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.82,1:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你\N{\rDefault Eng}Alright, I get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.77,1:15:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定要这么做吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.42,1:15:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不确定\N{\rDefault Eng}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.13,1:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种生物真是太神奇了\N{\rDefault Eng}This creature is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.52,1:15:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的基因也许承载了变种的关键\N{\rDefault Eng}Her genes could hold the key to mutation itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.28,1:15:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多\N{\rDefault Eng}I need more.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.42,1:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从巴黎街上刮下来的只有这么多了\N{\rDefault Eng}That's all they were able to scrape off the pavement in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.49,1:15:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了血以外的\N{\rDefault Eng}More than blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.19,1:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要脑组织\N{\rDefault Eng}I need brain tissue.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.13,1:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脊髓液\N{\rDefault Eng}Spinal fluid.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.20,1:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨髓\N{\rDefault Eng}Bone marrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.09,1:15:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象一下  能变形并根据目标改变的哨兵\N{\rDefault Eng}Imagine sentinels that could transform, adapt to any target.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.56,1:15:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我能抓住她\N{\rDefault Eng}If I just get my hands on her.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.71,1:16:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩能够大幅加快项目进程\N{\rDefault Eng}This girl could leap the program forward years,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.84,1:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能加快数十年\N{\rDefault Eng}decades into the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.11,1:16:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你儿子多大了  少校\N{\rDefault Eng}How old is your son now, Major?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.68,1:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Jason?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.06,1:16:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都快十岁了  不可思议吧\N{\rDefault Eng}He's coming up on 10 now if you can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.94,1:16:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有八年就要入伍了\N{\rDefault Eng}Eight years from fighting age.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.75,1:16:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有多少我们的儿子和弟兄\N{\rDefault Eng}And how many of our sons and brothers
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.31,1:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被装进尸袋送回家\N{\rDefault Eng}did we just ship home in body bags?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.62,1:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五万  五万五\N{\rDefault Eng}Maybe 50? 55000?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.71,1:16:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们的对手呢\N{\rDefault Eng}How many more on the other side?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.78,1:16:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有过\N{\rDefault Eng}Never before,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.84,1:16:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人类的历史上\N{\rDefault Eng}in all of human history,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.98,1:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有过什么能让全人类都团结起来\N{\rDefault Eng}has there been a cause which could unite us as a species.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.65,1:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有了\N{\rDefault Eng}Until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.21,1:16:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您非常憎恶变种人吧  博士\N{\rDefault Eng}You really hate mutants doctor, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.29,1:16:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恰恰相反  我因他们的能力而敬佩他们\N{\rDefault Eng}On the contrary, I rather admire them the things they can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.68,1:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得变种人是我们的救星\N{\rDefault Eng}I assume mutants as our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.93,1:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是共同的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}And common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.91,1:16:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们共同的斗争  为了战胜最终的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}Common struggle against the ultimate enemy..
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.68,1:16:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭绝\N{\rDefault Eng}Extinction.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.97,1:16:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我们的新朋友们\N{\rDefault Eng}I believe our new friends
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.02,1:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将帮助我们进入一个新的时代  比尔\N{\rDefault Eng}are going to help us usher in a new era, Bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.65,1:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有真实而持久的和平的新时代\N{\rDefault Eng}A new era of genuine and long lasting peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.00,1:17:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请注意  请注意\N{\rDefault Eng}Attention! Attention!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.38,1:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两小时后货物将离开\N{\rDefault Eng}Transport departure in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.47,1:17:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍\N{\rDefault Eng}Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.25,1:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两小时后货物将离开\N{\rDefault Eng}Transport departure begins in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.14,1:17:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上次下来是什么时候\N{\rDefault Eng}When was the last time you down here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.78,1:17:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们上次来找学生的时候  -很久了\N{\rDefault Eng}- Last time we went looking for students. - A life time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.99,1:17:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Welcome, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.50,1:18:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯受伤了  她动作不会太快\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven is wounded, she won't be moving fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.20,1:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久没伸展过这些肌肉了\N{\rDefault Eng}These are muscles I haven't stretched in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.10,1:18:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\rDefault Eng}Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.56,1:19:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.63,1:19:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯  没事了\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles, It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.06,1:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去检查发电机\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll go check the generator.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.62,1:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟机器无关  对吧\N{\rDefault Eng}It's not the machinery, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.93,1:19:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我做不到  我的思想  -你可以的\N{\rDefault Eng}- I can't do this, my mind... - Yes you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.83,1:19:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-它不听话  -就是有点生疏了\N{\rDefault Eng}- It won't take it. - It's just a little rusty.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.63,1:19:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂  这跟生疏没有关系\N{\rDefault Eng}You do not understand, It's not a question of being rusty.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.11,1:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以按下开关  可以转动把手\N{\rDefault Eng}I can flip the switches, I can turn the knobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.14,1:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我的力量来自这里  来自...\N{\rDefault Eng}But my power comes from here, comes from ..
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.43,1:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在它被毁了\N{\rDefault Eng}And it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.28,1:19:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉像自己的某个学生\N{\rDefault Eng}I feel like one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.50,1:19:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无助\N{\rDefault Eng}Helpless.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.17,1:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下来这里就是个错误\N{\rDefault Eng}It was a mistake coming down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.74,1:20:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把埃里克弄出来就是个错误\N{\rDefault Eng}It was a mistake freeing, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.18,1:20:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这整个事情就是个严重的错误\N{\rDefault Eng}This whole thing has been one bloody mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.38,1:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  罗根  但他们就不该派你回来\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm sorry, Logan, they sent back the wrong man.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.87,1:20:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\rDefault Eng}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.77,1:20:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该是我\N{\rDefault Eng}I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.12,1:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实本该是你自己来的\N{\rDefault Eng}Actually it was supposed to be you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.70,1:20:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我是唯一能撑得过传送的人\N{\rDefault Eng}But I was the only one who could physically make the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.11,1:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我们还有多长时间\N{\rDefault Eng}And I don't know how long we've got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.43,1:20:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道很久以后\N{\rDefault Eng}But I do know that a long time actually,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.86,1:20:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起很久以后\N{\rDefault Eng}a long time from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.56,1:20:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾是你彷徨无助的学生\N{\rDefault Eng}I was your lost helpless student.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.09,1:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你打开了我的思想\N{\rDefault Eng}and you unlocked my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.72,1:20:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我认清了自己\N{\rDefault Eng}You showed me what I was, you showed me what I could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.54,1:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道要怎么帮你\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't know how to do that for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.64,1:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我不知道\N{\rDefault Eng}you're right, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.61,1:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道有个人也许能做到\N{\rDefault Eng}But I know someone who might.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.72,1:20:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读我的记忆\N{\rDefault Eng}Look into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.87,1:20:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到我让脑波增幅器成了什么样\N{\rDefault Eng}You saw what I did to Cerebro.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.20,1:20:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想让我进入你脑子里的\N{\rDefault Eng}You don't want me inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.53,1:21:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么破坏是我没经历过的  相信我\N{\rDefault Eng}There's no damage you can do that has already been done, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.13,1:21:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-罗根  -琴\N{\rDefault Eng}- Hey, Logan. - Hey, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.74,1:21:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-杀了我  -我爱你\N{\rDefault Eng}- Kill me. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.91,1:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个...\N{\rDefault Eng}You're a...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.39,1:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的人\N{\rDefault Eng}poor man.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.35,1:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我的部分\N{\rDefault Eng}Look past me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.99,1:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看你的痛苦  我不想看你的未来\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't want your suffering! I don't want your future!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.61,1:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我的未来\N{\rDefault Eng}Pass my future.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.14,1:21:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找找你的未来\N{\rDefault Eng}Look for your future.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.95,1:21:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\rDefault Eng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.55,1:21:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\rDefault Eng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.25,1:21:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\rDefault Eng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.65,1:22:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.56,1:22:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.17,1:22:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们以后的样子吗\N{\rDefault Eng}So this is what become of us?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.73,1:22:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克说得没错\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.32,1:22:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人类把我们害成了这样\N{\rDefault Eng}Humanity does this to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.09,1:22:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非我们正确地引导他们\N{\rDefault Eng}Not if we show them a better path.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.26,1:22:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到现在还相信\N{\rDefault Eng}You still believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.47,1:23:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅因为有人跌倒迷了路\N{\rDefault Eng}Just because someone stumbles, loses their way,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.67,1:23:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不意味着他们会永远迷失\N{\rDefault Eng}it doesn't mean they're lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.09,1:23:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我们都需要一点帮助\N{\rDefault Eng}Sometimes we all need a little help.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.72,1:23:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再是以前的我了\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm not the man I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.76,1:23:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我使用了能力\N{\rDefault Eng}I opened my mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.34,1:23:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却几乎被压垮\N{\rDefault Eng}it almost overwhelms me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.94,1:23:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在害怕\N{\rDefault Eng}You're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.85,1:23:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑波增幅器能感觉到\N{\rDefault Eng}and Cerebro knows it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.52,1:23:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些声音\N{\rDefault Eng}All those voices...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.84,1:23:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多的痛苦\N{\rDefault Eng}So... much... pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.82,1:23:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕的不是他们的痛苦\N{\rDefault Eng}It's not their pain you're afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.50,1:23:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己的  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}It's yours, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.68,1:23:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这痛苦虽然可怕\N{\rDefault Eng}And as frightening as it may be,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.35,1:23:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却也能使你更加强壮\N{\rDefault Eng}that pain will make you stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.49,1:23:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能允许自己去感觉它\N{\rDefault Eng}If you allow yourself to feel it,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.71,1:23:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受它\N{\rDefault Eng}embrace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.59,1:23:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就能让你强大得超乎想象\N{\rDefault Eng}It will make you more powerful than you ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.95,1:23:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最伟大的天赋\N{\rDefault Eng}It's the greatest gift we have,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.43,1:24:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能承受痛苦而不被压垮\N{\rDefault Eng}to bear their pain without breaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.48,1:24:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人性的极致体现\N{\rDefault Eng}And it's born from the most human power,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.87,1:24:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望\N{\rDefault Eng}hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.62,1:24:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\rDefault Eng}Please,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.40,1:24:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.97,1:24:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你重拾希望\N{\rDefault Eng}we need you to hope again.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.33,1:24:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你要的了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.49,1:24:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供电恢复了\N{\rDefault Eng}Power is back on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.95,1:24:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.31,1:24:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是恢复了\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.32,1:26:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她失血太多了\N{\rDefault Eng}She's lost too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.37,1:26:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不能再这么下去了\N{\rDefault Eng}She can't keep going like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.53,1:26:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别无选择  波比\N{\rDefault Eng}We have no choice, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.20,1:26:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以唤醒他\N{\rDefault Eng}We can wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.11,1:26:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\rDefault Eng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.17,1:26:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们需要更多时间\N{\rDefault Eng}They need more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.01,1:26:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了过去\N{\rDefault Eng}I had a glimpse into the past,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.74,1:26:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们现在唤醒罗根情况可能会更糟\N{\rDefault Eng}if we wake Logan now we may set off an even darker course.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.90,1:26:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们需要更多时间\N{\rDefault Eng}They need more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.13,1:27:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯  停下\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.64,1:27:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑了\N{\rDefault Eng}Stop running.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.57,1:27:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.90,1:27:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\rDefault Eng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.08,1:27:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家里\N{\rDefault Eng}Back at the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.18,1:27:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该回来\N{\rDefault Eng}Where you should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.21,1:27:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你回来\N{\rDefault Eng}I need you to come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.11,1:27:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己该做什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I know what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.86,1:27:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你杀了特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}If you kill Trask,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.84,1:27:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有更多像他一样的人出现\N{\rDefault Eng}You will be creating countless more just like him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.65,1:27:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就把他们也杀了\N{\rDefault Eng}Then I'll kill them too.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.84,1:27:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是埃里克的想法  不是你的\N{\rDefault Eng}Those are Erik's words, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.15,1:27:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一同长大的女孩不会杀戮\N{\rDefault Eng}The girl I grew up with wasn't capable of killing,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.79,1:27:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很善良  公正并充满同情心\N{\rDefault Eng}she was good, fair, full of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.78,1:27:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有同情心  但不是对特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}I have compassion, just not for Trask.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.05,1:27:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀了太多我们的同伴\N{\rDefault Eng}He's murdered too many of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.75,1:28:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止她  查尔斯  进入她的大脑\N{\rDefault Eng}Shut her down Charles, get in her head.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.85,1:28:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不让我进去  我快坚持不住了\N{\rDefault Eng}She's not letting me in I'm barely holding on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.52,1:28:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不够强大\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm not strong enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.65,1:28:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道特拉斯克做了什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I know what Trask has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.05,1:28:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可杀了他也不能让他们复生\N{\rDefault Eng}But, killing him will not bring them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.97,1:28:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让你陷入万劫不复的境地\N{\rDefault Eng}It will set you on a path from which there is no return,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.82,1:28:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和他们将陷入无休止的杀戮\N{\rDefault Eng}an endless cycle of killing us and them,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.73,1:28:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到什么都不剩\N{\rDefault Eng}till there is nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.41,1:28:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们可以现在就阻止这一切\N{\rDefault Eng}But we can stop it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.58,1:28:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我\N{\rDefault Eng}You and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.31,1:28:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你必须回家来\N{\rDefault Eng}You just have to come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.63,1:28:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须\N{\rDefault Eng}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.85,1:28:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是一点都没变  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}You haven't changed at all, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.45,1:28:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了\N{\rDefault Eng}Like I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.87,1:28:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己该做什么\N{\rDefault Eng}I know exactly what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.64,1:29:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\rDefault Eng}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.93,1:29:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在机场登机\N{\rDefault Eng}She's at an airport boarding a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.37,1:29:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪的飞机\N{\rDefault Eng}Plane to where?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.89,1:29:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华盛顿特区\N{\rDefault Eng}Washington DC.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.15,1:29:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\rDefault Eng}Hey guys,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.06,1:29:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你们看样东西\N{\rDefault Eng}there is something I need to show to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.05,1:29:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我设计的一个系统\N{\rDefault Eng}It's just a system I designed,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.53,1:29:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来收录巴黎事件相关新闻的\N{\rDefault Eng}to record any news about Paris,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.62,1:29:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖了全部三家广播网和公共广播公司\N{\rDefault Eng}over all 3 networks and PBS.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.40,1:29:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部三家\N{\rDefault Eng}All three?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.36,1:29:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  还有公共广播公司\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, and PBS.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.13,1:29:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我录到了什么\N{\rDefault Eng}Look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.72,1:29:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  美国总统\N{\rDefault Eng}Tomorrow in front of the White House
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.21,1:29:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将在白宫门口发表声明\N{\rDefault Eng}the president will make his announcement.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.08,1:29:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时出席的还将有国防部长布莱尔\N{\rDefault Eng}He'll be joined by Secretary of Defense Blair.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.39,1:29:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及著名科学家玻利瓦尔·特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}And has even sought the help of renowned scientist Bolivar Trask.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.09,1:29:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将担任总统对抗变种人问题的特别顾问\N{\rDefault Eng}His special adviser to combat this mutant issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.16,1:29:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫将\N{\rDefault Eng}The White House is....
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.92,1:29:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯没有意识到  如果她在\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven doesn't realize but if she kills Trask
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.29,1:29:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种全球瞩目的情况下杀掉特拉斯克\N{\rDefault Eng}at an event like that with the whole world watching...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.44,1:29:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我这趟就白跑了\N{\rDefault Eng}Then I came a long way for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.39,1:30:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不止这些  我在一篇报道中看到\N{\rDefault Eng}And there's more bad news, I saw in a report.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.78,1:30:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在巴黎找到了她的血迹\N{\rDefault Eng}They found traces of her blood in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.85,1:30:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能已经有她的DNA了\N{\rDefault Eng}For all we know they already have her DNA.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只需要这个\N{\rDefault Eng}Which is all they need.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.02,1:30:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能在未来造出哨兵\N{\rDefault Eng}To create the sentinels in the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.64,1:30:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量子物理学中有个理论称时间是永恒的\N{\rDefault Eng}Now there's a theory in quantum physics that time is immutable.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.68,1:30:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就像河流  你可以丢个卵石进去\N{\rDefault Eng}It's like a river, you can throw a pebble and
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.99,1:30:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽会激起涟漪  但水流总会自我修正\N{\rDefault Eng}it will create a ripple but the current always corrects itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.79,1:30:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你做什么\N{\rDefault Eng}No matter what you do
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.50,1:30:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始终无法改变水流的方向\N{\rDefault Eng}the river just keeps flowing in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.99,1:30:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.30,1:30:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说\N{\rDefault Eng}What I was saying is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.51,1:30:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一战争是无可避免的呢\N{\rDefault Eng}what if the war is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.24,1:30:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一她注定要杀死特拉斯克呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What if she's meant to kill Trask.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.06,1:30:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一这就是她的本质呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What if this is just simply who she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.59,1:30:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅因为有人跌倒迷了路\N{\rDefault Eng}Just because someone stumbles, loses their way,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.93,1:30:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不意味着他们会永远迷失\N{\rDefault Eng}doesn't mean they're lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.64,1:30:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信那个理论  汉克\N{\rDefault Eng}I don't believe that theory, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.28,1:30:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不相信这就是她的本质\N{\rDefault Eng}And I can not believe that is who she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.94,1:31:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备飞机  我们去华盛顿\N{\rDefault Eng}Ready the plane we're going to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.22,1:31:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20\b0\pos(192,215)}华   盛   顿   特   区
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.33,1:32:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\rDefault Eng}You alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.82,1:32:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会好起来的\N{\rDefault Eng}Getting there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.75,1:32:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管今天发生什么\N{\rDefault Eng}Whatever happens today,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.68,1:32:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须向我保证一件事\N{\rDefault Eng}I need you to promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.33,1:32:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看过我的记忆  看到了很多不幸\N{\rDefault Eng}You looked into my mind and you've seen a lot of bad but,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.25,1:32:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也看到了好的回忆\N{\rDefault Eng}you've seen the good too.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.02,1:32:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些X战警\N{\rDefault Eng}The X-Men.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.93,1:32:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应我你会找到我们\N{\rDefault Eng}Promise me you'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.36,1:32:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的力量  将我们聚集起来\N{\rDefault Eng}Use your power, bring us together.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.93,1:32:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指引我们  领导我们\N{\rDefault Eng}Guide us. Lead us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.70,1:32:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风女\N{\rDefault Eng}Storm,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.29,1:32:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯考特\N{\rDefault Eng}Scott,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.55,1:32:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴\N{\rDefault Eng}Jean.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.40,1:33:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住这些名字\N{\rDefault Eng}Remember those names.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.45,1:33:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有很多人\N{\rDefault Eng}There's so many of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.48,1:33:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会需要你的  教授\N{\rDefault Eng}We will need you, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.71,1:33:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的\N{\rDefault Eng}I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.32,1:33:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽力就够了\N{\rDefault Eng}Your best is enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.93,1:33:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\rDefault Eng}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.61,1:33:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有12辆运输器过来了  还有16公里\N{\rDefault Eng}12 carriers inbound, 10 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.45,1:33:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们找到我们了\N{\rDefault Eng}They found us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.13,1:34:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  成千上万的民众将聚集在这里\N{\rDefault Eng}Thousands of people will be gathered here today,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.33,1:34:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们从世界各地赶来见证这一历史时刻\N{\rDefault Eng}they come from all over the world to witness history
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.88,1:34:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时还有来自至少50个国家的记者们\N{\rDefault Eng}along with news crews from at least 50 different countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.04,1:34:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rDefault Eng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.99,1:34:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看看你们的邀请函吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can I see your invitations please?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.16,1:34:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes, you may.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.63,1:34:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩是和我一起的\N{\rDefault Eng}These two are with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.00,1:34:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请  -谢谢\N{\rDefault Eng}- Go ahead. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.74,1:34:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗根\N{\rDefault Eng}Logan.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.07,1:34:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请这边走  先生\N{\rDefault Eng}Please, this way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.39,1:35:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没找到她  但她肯定在\N{\rDefault Eng}I haven't found her yet but she has to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.47,1:35:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请美国总统\N{\rDefault Eng}President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.93,1:35:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的美国同胞们\N{\rDefault Eng}My fellow Americans,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.94,1:35:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们面临着历史上最大的威胁\N{\rDefault Eng}today we face the greatest threat in our history.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.86,1:35:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}Mutants.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.96,1:35:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.98,1:35:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做好了应对这一威胁的准备\N{\rDefault Eng}We have prepared for this threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.45,1:35:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引用罗伯特·奥本海默的不朽名言\N{\rDefault Eng}In the immortal words of Robert Oppenheimer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.17,1:35:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看\N{\rDefault Eng}Behold.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.96,1:35:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界将从此不同了\N{\rDefault Eng}The world will never be the same again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.28,1:36:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.55,1:36:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你管不了的\N{\rDefault Eng}No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.36,1:37:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\rDefault Eng}Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.69,1:37:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹们  这是为了你们\N{\rDefault Eng}This is for you, brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.16,1:37:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.97,1:37:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到她了\N{\rDefault Eng}I have her.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.53,1:37:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Let me go, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.00,1:37:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那  看见了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}There. You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.70,1:37:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台左边那个特勤人员\N{\rDefault Eng}Secret service man, left to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.73,1:37:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-看见了  -快去\N{\rDefault Eng}- Got it. - Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.93,1:37:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈干什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.33,1:37:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没叫你启动它们\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't tell you to activate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.97,1:37:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没启动\N{\rDefault Eng}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.44,1:38:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯  请听我说\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven, please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.07,1:38:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可以让他们重新认识我们\N{\rDefault Eng}We've been given a second chance to define who we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.22,1:38:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做\N{\rDefault Eng}Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.98,1:38:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们  你们不能过去\N{\rDefault Eng}Gentlemen, you cannot pass this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.09,1:38:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们阻止不了这么多\N{\rDefault Eng}We can't stop that many.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.98,1:38:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能\N{\rDefault Eng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.96,1:38:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们可以拖延它们\N{\rDefault Eng}But, we can slow them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.70,1:39:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Erik!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.26,1:40:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  快走\N{\rDefault Eng}Move it ! Come on let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.37,1:40:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风女\N{\rDefault Eng}Storm!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.71,1:40:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入三级戒备状态\N{\rDefault Eng}Take us to Def-con 3.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.35,1:40:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我们现在是红色警报\N{\rDefault Eng}Mr. President we are code red.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.69,1:40:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空中防御就绪\N{\rDefault Eng}Air defense ready now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.75,1:40:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才到底怎么回事\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell happened out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.21,1:40:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会解决的\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.29,1:40:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前就这么说过\N{\rDefault Eng}You said that before,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.54,1:40:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本要发表声明的\N{\rDefault Eng}I wanted to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.81,1:41:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在整个世界都知道我们无法保护他们了\N{\rDefault Eng}Now the whole goddamn world knows we can't protect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.79,1:41:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会解决的\N{\rDefault Eng}I will fix it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.10,1:41:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好能解决\N{\rDefault Eng}You damn well better.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.19,1:42:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Charles!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.18,1:43:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Is everybody okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.51,1:43:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风女\N{\rDefault Eng}Storm!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.52,1:43:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心身后\N{\rDefault Eng}Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.21,1:44:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送我过去\N{\rDefault Eng}Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.99,1:44:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许不该问这种事\N{\rDefault Eng}I'm probably not supposed to ask this kind of a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.08,1:45:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在未来  我活下来了吗\N{\rDefault Eng}But in the future, do I make it?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.12,1:45:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rDefault Eng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.09,1:45:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们可以改变未来  对吧\N{\rDefault Eng}But we can change that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.75,1:45:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去完成你的使命吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Do what you were made for.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.83,1:45:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(140,81)\clip(121,80,158,97)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\b1\1a&HFF&\bord40\shad0\3c&H04008C&}变种人
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.92,1:45:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(218,161)\clip(200,160,235,177)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\b1\1a&HFF&\bord40\shad0\3c&H04008C&}变种人
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.60,1:45:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪\N{\rDefault Eng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.37,1:45:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我  你去吧\N{\rDefault Eng}I got this. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.72,1:46:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  不\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh dear God, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.14,1:46:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为幸存者的日子到此为止了\N{\rDefault Eng}So much for being a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.94,1:47:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个变种人\N{\rDefault Eng}One of them is in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.94,1:47:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不\N{\rDefault Eng}No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.06,1:47:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别杀它\N{\rDefault Eng}Don't kill it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.21,1:47:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要活的\N{\rDefault Eng}I need it alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.00,1:47:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这他妈到底怎么回事\N{\rDefault Eng}What the hell has happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.14,1:49:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们造了这些武器来消灭我们\N{\rDefault Eng}You built these weapons to destroy us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.46,1:49:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\rDefault Eng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.65,1:49:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们害怕我们的天赋\N{\rDefault Eng}Because you're afraid of our gifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.24,1:49:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们与你们不同\N{\rDefault Eng}Because we are different.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.86,1:49:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类总是惧怕异类\N{\rDefault Eng}Humanity has always feared that which is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.04,1:49:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在要告诉你们  告诉世界\N{\rDefault Eng}But I'm here to tell you, tell the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.94,1:49:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该怕我们\N{\rDefault Eng}You're right to fear us.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.61,1:49:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是未来\N{\rDefault Eng}We are the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.02,1:49:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将会继承这片土地\N{\rDefault Eng}We are the ones who will inherit this earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.90,1:49:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何试图阻止我们的人\N{\rDefault Eng}And anyone who stands in our way,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.00,1:49:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都将遭遇你们面前这些人的下场\N{\rDefault Eng}will suffer the same fate as these men you see before you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.07,1:49:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天本是你们要展现能力的日子\N{\rDefault Eng}Today was meant to be a display of your power.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.71,1:49:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在给你们看看\N{\rDefault Eng}Instead I give you a glimpse
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.86,1:50:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的种族可以给你们带来的毁灭\N{\rDefault Eng}of the devastation my race can unleash upon yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.78,1:50:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是对世界的警告吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Let this be a warning to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.68,1:50:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而对我的变种人兄弟姐妹们\N{\rDefault Eng}And to my mutant brothers and sisters out there,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.30,1:50:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说\N{\rDefault Eng}I say this:
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.24,1:50:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不用躲藏\N{\rDefault Eng}no more hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.22,1:50:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不用受苦\N{\rDefault Eng}No more suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.84,1:50:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已在羞辱和恐惧的阴影下生活太久了\N{\rDefault Eng}You've lived in a shadows in shame and fear too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.81,1:50:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出来吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.41,1:50:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入我的行列  为我们变种人而战\N{\rDefault Eng}Join me, fight together in the brotherhood of our kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.02,1:50:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的明天\N{\rDefault Eng}A new tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.84,1:50:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始于今日\N{\rDefault Eng}that starts today.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.87,1:50:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们浪费了这么多年彼此对抗  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}All those years wasted fighting each other, Charles
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.41,1:50:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了那些许珍贵的岁月\N{\rDefault Eng}to have a precious few of them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.86,1:51:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总统先生  -退后  我说了  退后\N{\rDefault Eng}- Mr. President. - Stand down ! I said stand down!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.00,1:51:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想表明态度吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You want to make a statement?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.96,1:51:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我  没问题\N{\rDefault Eng}Kill me...fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.93,1:51:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但把其他人放了\N{\rDefault Eng}But spare everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.57,1:52:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是英雄之举啊  总统先生\N{\rDefault Eng}Very heroic, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.50,1:52:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却从未打算放过我们的人\N{\rDefault Eng}But you had no intention of sparing any of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.25,1:52:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们种族的未来就从现在开始\N{\rDefault Eng}The future of our species begins now.
