Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.96,1:52:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\clip(111,186,148,205)\pos(130,189)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\b1\1a&HFF&\bord40\shad0\3c&H04008C&\t(106,106,\3a&HFF&)\t(190,190,\3a0)\t(273,273,\3a&HFF&)\t(315,315,\3a0)}变种人
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.06,1:52:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前的枪法可更准\N{\rDefault Eng}You used to be a better shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.27,1:52:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  现在依旧很准\N{\rDefault Eng}Trust me, I still I'm.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.32,1:53:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出我的思想  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Get out of my head, Charles!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.10,1:53:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}Raven,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.81,1:53:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让变种人在今天成为世界的敌人\N{\rDefault Eng}please do not make us the enemy today.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.06,1:53:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看四周  我们已经是了\N{\rDefault Eng}Look around you, we already are.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.47,1:53:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不全是\N{\rDefault Eng}Not all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.35,1:53:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你目前为止所做的\N{\rDefault Eng}All you've done so far
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.61,1:53:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在救这些人的命\N{\rDefault Eng}is save the lives of these men.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.78,1:53:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以引导他们\N{\rDefault Eng}You can show them a better path.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.95,1:53:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她弄昏  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}Shut her down, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.75,1:53:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们认识起  我就一直在试图控制你\N{\rDefault Eng}I've been trying to control you ever since the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.80,1:53:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看现在的结果\N{\rDefault Eng}And look what that's got us.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.84,1:53:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要发生的一切\N{\rDefault Eng}Everything that happens now,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.37,1:53:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都由你来决定\N{\rDefault Eng}is in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.65,1:53:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你  瑞雯\N{\rDefault Eng}I have faith in you, Raven.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.08,1:55:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把他交给你了  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}He's all yours, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.77,1:55:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我交给他们  我就死定了\N{\rDefault Eng}If you let them have me I'm as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.53,1:56:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\rDefault Eng}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.60,1:56:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rDefault Eng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.20,1:56:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了  老朋友\N{\rDefault Eng}Good-bye, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.40,1:56:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  埃里克\N{\rDefault Eng}Good-bye, Erik.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:44.68,1:56:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定要让他们走吗\N{\rDefault Eng}You sure you should let them go?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.73,1:56:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.62,1:56:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他们存有希望\N{\rDefault Eng}I have hope for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.70,1:56:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来有一天  汉克\N{\rDefault Eng}It's going to be a time, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.71,1:56:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都会重聚\N{\rDefault Eng}When we're all together.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:00.45,1:57:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那罗根呢\N{\rDefault Eng}What about Logan?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.06,1:58:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  罗根  你起晚了\N{\rDefault Eng}Good morning, Logan. Late start.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.78,1:58:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受午餐吧  干得好\N{\rDefault Eng}Have a good lunch time. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.11,1:58:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -干得很漂亮\N{\rDefault Eng}- Thank you. - Very good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:50.18,1:58:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风女\N{\rDefault Eng}Storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.85,1:59:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴\N{\rDefault Eng}Jean.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:25.37,1:59:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗根\N{\rDefault Eng}Hi, Logan.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.00,1:59:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.36,1:59:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这\N{\rDefault Eng}You're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.49,1:59:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我还能在哪\N{\rDefault Eng}Where else would I be?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:40.62,1:59:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠着点  伙计\N{\rDefault Eng}Easy, pal.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.15,1:59:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事怎么就变不了呢\N{\rDefault Eng}Some things never change.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.12,1:59:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  斯考特\N{\rDefault Eng}Good to see you, Scott.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.52,1:59:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见  琴\N{\rDefault Eng}See you later, Jean.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.21,1:59:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\N{\rDefault Eng}Professor.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.00,2:00:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗根\N{\rDefault Eng}Logan.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.54,2:00:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都还好吧\N{\rDefault Eng}Is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.29,2:00:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.84,2:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\rDefault Eng}Yeah, I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.39,2:00:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做到了\N{\rDefault Eng}You did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.69,2:00:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到什么\N{\rDefault Eng}Did what?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.66,2:00:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗根  你不是要教课吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Logan, don't you have a class to teach?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.53,2:00:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我来教课  -是啊\N{\rDefault Eng}- A class to teach? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.23,2:00:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史课\N{\rDefault Eng}History.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.89,2:00:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史\N{\rDefault Eng}History?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.31,2:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我还真需要你帮点忙\N{\rDefault Eng}Actually, I could use some help with that.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.36,2:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮什么忙\N{\rDefault Eng}Help with what?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.07,2:00:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1973年后的所有历史\N{\rDefault Eng}Pretty much everything after 1973.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.31,2:00:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我知道的历史跟你有些不同\N{\rDefault Eng}I think history I know is a little different.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.92,2:00:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\rDefault Eng}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.29,2:01:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你真高兴  查尔斯\N{\rDefault Eng}It's good to see you, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.42,2:01:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到大家真好\N{\rDefault Eng}It's good to see everyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.39,2:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是\N{\rDefault Eng}Well,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.42,2:01:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要遵守诺言嘛\N{\rDefault Eng}I had a promise to keep.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.66,2:01:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱俩得好好叙叙旧\N{\rDefault Eng}You and I have lot of catching up to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.89,2:01:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是\N{\rDefault Eng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.09,2:01:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记得的最后一件事是什么\N{\rDefault Eng}What is the last thing you remember?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.27,2:01:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溺水\N{\rDefault Eng}Drowning.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.65,2:01:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去\N{\rDefault Eng}The past,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.11,2:01:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个崭新和不确定的世界\N{\rDefault Eng}a new and uncertain world.
