Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.56,2:01:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个充满无限可能\N{\rDefault Eng}A world of endless possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.49,2:02:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和无穷结果的世界\N{\rDefault Eng}And infinite outcomes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.29,2:02:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz18.017\pos(196,84)\fad(330,0)\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H231F1E&} 特拉斯克因出售军事机密被捕
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.51,2:02:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\rDefault Eng}Can we?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.59,2:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着\N{\rDefault Eng}Oh, he is alive!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.77,2:02:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在呼吸\N{\rDefault Eng}He is breathing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.46,2:02:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数的选择决定了我们的命运\N{\rDefault Eng}Countless choices define our fate.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.16,2:02:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个选择  每个时刻\N{\rDefault Eng}Each choice, each moment,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.85,2:02:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是时间长河中的一个涟漪\N{\rDefault Eng}a ripple in the river of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.48,2:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我们怎么处置他  史崔克少校\N{\rDefault Eng}What do you want us to do with him, Major Stryker?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.13,2:02:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有足够多的涟漪  就能改变潮流\N{\rDefault Eng}Enough ripples and you change the tide.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.65,2:02:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他交给我吧\N{\rDefault Eng}I'll take him from here.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.11,2:02:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为未来永远不会真成定数\N{\rDefault Eng}For the future is never truly set.
